Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔在哪里？我得和他谈谈\N{\rEng}Where's Michael? I gotta to talk to him, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,理清楚几件事，我不能排队等着\N{\rEng}get a few things straight, and I can't wait on line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你先去看你的孩子\N{\rEng}You go see your children first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再操心排队见你哥哥的事\N{\rEng}Then you worry about waiting on line to see your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,和别人一样\N{\rEng}Like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们女士们\N{\rEng}Ladies and gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克，醒醒…\N{\rEng}Frank, wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一位最尊贵的来宾 想要说几句话\N{\rEng}A most distinguished guest would like to say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,请各位欢迎 内华达州的参议员帕特·葛瑞\N{\rEng}Would you please welcome Senator Pat Geary of the State of Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还有葛瑞太太\N{\rEng}And there is Mrs. Geary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,非常谢谢各位先生女士\N{\rEng}Thank you very much, Ladies and Gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是个非常快乐的日子\N{\rEng}This is a very, very happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对于我和我妻子盖瑞太太而言\N{\rEng}for me and my wife Mrs. Geary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们极少回来内华达州\N{\rEng}We see Nevada far too seldom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但特别在今天我们可以…\N{\rEng}But particular today when we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以和老朋友相聚，可以结交新朋友\N{\rEng}we can join with old friends, we can make new friends
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还可以共同庆祝…\N{\rEng}and we help celebrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一个年轻人首度领圣餐礼\N{\rEng}a young man's first Communion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也要谢谢那孩子的家庭 对于本州慷慨的捐献\N{\rEng}And also to thank that boy's family for a magnificent contribution to the State.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我手上有张支票\N{\rEng}I have here in my hand a cheque
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,写给州立大学\N{\rEng}made out to the university,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而且捐款数额惊人\N{\rEng}and it is a magnificent endowment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,捐赠名义是\N{\rEng}in the name of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼·维多·柯利昂尼\N{\rEng}Anthony Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,支票由那位年轻人的父母签字\N{\rEng}And the cheque is signed by that young man's parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们应该认识一下\N{\rEng}whom I think we should recognise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，帕特，凯伊伊，请站起来\N{\rEng}Mike, Pat, Kay. stand up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来，让大伙们看到你们\N{\rEng}Stand up, let the folks see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，希望大家和我一起…\N{\rEng}Folks, I want you to join me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,给予迈克尔·柯利昂尼先生夫人一次内华达式的感谢\N{\rEng}in giving a real Nevada thank you to Mr. and Mrs. Michael Corleone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们同时还有一个特别外加节目\N{\rEng}We also have, as a special added attraction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,西耶华男孩合唱团\N{\rEng}the Sierra Boys Choir,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们挑选了一首特别的歌\N{\rEng}who have chosen a certain special song
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,以及特别的编曲，向我们的主人致意\N{\rEng}and a special arrangement to honour their host
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔·柯利昂尼先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们！\N{\rEng}Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,牌匾\N{\rEng}The plaque.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，各位，你们拍到没？\N{\rEng}Okay, fellows, did you get that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好，这就行，好了\N{\rEng}Okay, that's good. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，参议员，就你和柯利昂尼太太\N{\rEng}Now, Senator, just you and Mrs. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 那样就行了\N{\rEng}Okay that's enough, Senator
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请把支票给我\N{\rEng}Give me the cheque.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,拿高点让我们看得见\N{\rEng}higher,so we can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的律师汤姆·黑根\N{\rEng}My lawyer Tom Hagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,葛瑞参议员\N{\rEng}Senator Geary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他通过你的手下特恩布尔安排这整件事的\N{\rEng}He's the one arranged this whole thing through your man Turnbull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好，好\N{\rEng}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\rEng}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在我印象中 你和我将会单独谈话\N{\rEng}Well I was under the impression that you and I would talk alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人我可以托付性命，参议员\N{\rEng}I trust these men with my life, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我要求他们离开，那会是一种侮辱\N{\rEng}If I would ask them to leave, it would be an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…\N{\rEng}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全没问题\N{\rEng}it's perfectly all right with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但我得告诉你 我是个直率的人\N{\rEng}but I should tell you that I am a blunt man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我打算 跟你说得很坦率\N{\rEng}and I intend to speak very frankly to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也许 比以前任何我这个地位的人跟你说话都坦率\N{\rEng}Maybe more frankly than anyone in my position has ever talked to you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼家族在内华达做得很好\N{\rEng}The Corleone family has done well in Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你拥有或者说控制了 维加斯的两家主要酒店\N{\rEng}You own, or you control, two major hotels in Vegas,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在里诺还有一家\N{\rEng}and one in Reno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,执照是新法规前就有的\N{\rEng}The licences were grandfathered in,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在赌博委员会是没有问题\N{\rEng}so there was no problem with the Gaming Commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我的消息来源告诉我…\N{\rEng}Now my sources tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你计划开始去对付“塔皮盖拉”\N{\rEng}you plan to make a move against the Tropigala.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们告诉我说 在一周之内\N{\rEng}They tell me that, within a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要把克林蒙扫地出门\N{\rEng}you're going to move Klingman out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不小的扩充\N{\rEng}That's quite an expansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，它会带给你一个小小的技术问题\N{\rEng}However, it will leave you with a little technical problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,执照仍然会在克林蒙的名下\N{\rEng}The licence will still be in Klingman's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,特恩布尔是个能干的人啊\N{\rEng}Turnbull is a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，我们…我们废话少说吧\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, let's cut out the bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想花费过多时间在这里\N{\rEng}I don't want to spend more time here than I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以拥有执照\N{\rEng}You can have the licence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,价格是25万美元\N{\rEng}The price is 250,000 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,加上每个月总收入的5%\N{\rEng}Plus monthly pay five per cent of the gross
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所有四家酒店的，柯利昂尼先生\N{\rEng}of all four hotels, Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,执照的价格少于2万美元，我说得对吗？\N{\rEng}Now, the price for the licence is less than 20,000 dollars, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对的\N{\rEng}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那我为何要考虑比那付得更多呢？\N{\rEng}Now, why would I ever considered pay more than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我成心要压榨你\N{\rEng}Because I intend to squeeze you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢你们这种人\N{\rEng}I don't like your kind of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢看见你在这个干净的国家出现，梳着…\N{\rEng}I don't like to see you come out to this clean country in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,油光光的头发\N{\rEng}oily hair
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着那身丝质西装\N{\rEng}dressed up in those silk suits
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,努力把自己假扮成正派的美国人\N{\rEng}and try to pass yourselves off as decent Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟你做生意，但是…\N{\rEng}I'll do business with you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我鄙视你的伪装\N{\rEng}the fact is that I despise your masquerade,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你那不诚实的装模作样\N{\rEng}the dishonest way you pose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你他妈的整个家族\N{\rEng}Yourself, and your whole fucking family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员\N{\rEng}Senator...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我俩都同样的有部分伪善\N{\rEng}...we're both part of the same hypocrisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝不要以为可以适用于我的家庭\N{\rEng}But never think it applies to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧\N{\rEng}All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人就是得玩小把戏\N{\rEng}Some people have to play little games.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你玩你的\N{\rEng}You play yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这么说吧，你付钱给我，因为那是你的利益所在\N{\rEng}So, let's say that you'll pay me because it's in your interest to pay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但明天中午前我要你的答复和钱\N{\rEng}But I want your answer and the money by noon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事\N{\rEng}One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不准你再联系我，永远\N{\rEng}Don't you contact me again, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,从今以后，你跟特恩布尔打交道\N{\rEng}From now on you deal with Turnbull.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,打开那门，小子\N{\rEng}Open that door, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员\N{\rEng}Senator
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意的话，你现在就能得到我的答复\N{\rEng}you can have my answer now if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的条件是：\N{\rEng}My offer is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,连赌博执照的费用也不给\N{\rEng}Not even the fee for the gaming licence
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你个人能提供那项费用 我会感激的\N{\rEng}which I would appreciate if you would put up personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,午安，先生们\N{\rEng}Good afternoon, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们，我不知道你们在外面\N{\rEng}Ladies! I didn't know you were out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的，我们得走了，我们已经迟了30分钟了\N{\rEng}Honey, we have to go. We're 30 minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？真遗憾\N{\rEng}Really? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼太太，我们很愉快，谢谢你\N{\rEng}Mrs. Corleone, it's been delightful. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们的荣幸 非常感谢\N{\rEng}It was our pleasure. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,和你谈话真是愉快\N{\rEng}It was wonderful talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多\N{\rEng}Fredo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多，你这个臭小子\N{\rEng}Fredo, you son-of-a-bitch,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你气色真好\N{\rEng}you look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克·潘坦吉利\N{\rEng}Frank Pentangeli!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你永远不会来西部 你这大混蛋\N{\rEng}I thought you was never coming out west you big bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我总得照顾我的手下 不是吗？\N{\rEng}I've got to check on my boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多 这里的食物是怎么回事？\N{\rEng}Hey, Fredo, wshat's with the food around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了？ - 穿白色上衣的孩子端给我的\N{\rEng}- What's the matter? - A kid comes up to mein a white jacket,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,给了我几片饼干还有碎鹅肝，说那是“坎纳披”\N{\rEng}gives me a Ritz cracker, and uh, chopped liver, he says Canapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我说“坎纳披”个屁，那只是饼干配上碎鹅肝\N{\rEng}I said uh, uh, can o' peas my ass, that's a Ritz cracker and chopped liver!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，是不是随便谁…\N{\rEng}Hey, does anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.62,Chs,,0,0,0,,这里有烧烤{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,把胡椒和香肠拿出来啊\N{\rEng}Bring out the peppers and sardines!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.19,Chs,,0,0,0,,把胡椒和香肠拿出来{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，看到你让我想起了 纽约的昔日时光\N{\rEng}Seeing you reminds me of New York in the old days!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，弗雷多，你还记得威利·奇齐吗？\N{\rEng}Hey, Fredo.You remember Willi Cicci
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和老家伙克里门萨一起在布鲁克林…\N{\rEng}who was with old man Clemenza in Brooklyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对他的事都很难过，弗兰基\N{\rEng}We were all upset about that, Franki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,心脏病发作 对吧？\N{\rEng}Heart attack, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那不是心脏病发作\N{\rEng}No, that was no heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…那是我来这里见你弟弟麦克的原因\N{\rEng}That was...That's what I'm here to see your brother Mike about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是他是怎么回事？ - 什么意思？\N{\rEng}- But what's with him? - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说我要怎么做？我是不是得先有一封介绍信？\N{\rEng}I mean what do I have to do? Do I have to get a letter of introduction
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,才能得到个座位？\N{\rEng}to get a sit-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你不能进去见麦克？\N{\rEng}You can't get in to see Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他要我在会客厅等着\N{\rEng}He's got me waiting in a lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰尼·欧拉\N{\rEng}Johnny Ola.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔·奈利\N{\rEng}Al Neri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.15,Chs,,0,0,0,,（意大利语）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你认得我的律师汤姆·黑根 约翰尼·欧拉\N{\rEng}Do you know my lawyer Tom Hagen?Johnny Ola.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我老早就认得汤姆了\N{\rEng}Sure, I remember Tom from the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,洛可，这是什么？\N{\rEng}Rocco, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是迈阿密的橙子\N{\rEng}It's an orange from Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要不你去招呼一下约翰尼的人，他们看来像是饿了\N{\rEng}Why don't you take care of Johnny's men. They look like they might be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰尼！\N{\rEng}Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\rEng}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆不会陪我们坐，约翰尼\N{\rEng}Tom's not gonna sitting with us, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他只处理一些特殊领域的家族事务\N{\rEng}He only handles specific areas of the family business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆\N{\rEng}Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 麦克\N{\rEng}Sure, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝什么，约翰尼？\N{\rEng}What are you drinking, Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,茴香酒\N{\rEng}Anisette.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,茴香酒\N{\rEng}Anisette.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么需要，麦克，我就在外面好吗？\N{\rEng}If you need anything, Mike, I'll be outside, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只要告诉洛可我们在等他，汤姆\N{\rEng}Just tell Rocco we're waiting, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚在迈阿密见过罗斯先生\N{\rEng}I just left Mr. Roth in Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他的健康如何？\N{\rEng}How is his health?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不，并不好\N{\rEng}Na, it's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做些什么吗? 能送他什么吗\N{\rEng}Is there anything I can do? Anything I can send?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们感激你的关心，麦克\N{\rEng}We appreciate your concen, Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你的敬意\N{\rEng}and your respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你感兴趣的那家赌场\N{\rEng}That casino you interested in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,登记的所有人是：\N{\rEng}the registered owners are:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,雅各布·劳伦斯和亚伦·巴克利，都是比佛利山的律师\N{\rEng}Jacob Lawrence, Allan Barclay. Both Beverly Hills attorneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的所有人是 克里夫兰的湖村路集团\N{\rEng}The real owners are the old Lakeville Road group, Cleveland.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我们在迈阿密的朋友\N{\rEng}and our friend in Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,迈耶·克林蒙负责经营\N{\rEng}Meyer Klingman runs the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他也拥有一部分股权，他做得还好\N{\rEng}he runs a piece of it too, he does alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.16,0:23:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我接到指示告诉你\N{\rEng}but I've been instructed to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,若你想让弄走克林蒙\N{\rEng}that if you move Klingman out,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在迈阿密的朋友会支持的\N{\rEng}our friend in Miami will go along.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他非常好心\N{\rEng}It's very kind of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉他 我极为感激\N{\rEng}You tell him it's greatly appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,海门·罗斯总是为他的搭档赚钱\N{\rEng}Hyman Roth always makes money for his partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一个接一个\N{\rEng}One by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的老朋友都走了\N{\rEng}our old friends are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,死了\N{\rEng}Death
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,自然死亡或非自然\N{\rEng}natural or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.94,0:23:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,入狱、流亡\N{\rEng}prison, deported...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,海门·罗斯是唯一剩下的\N{\rEng}Hyman Roth is the only one left,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他总是替他的搭档赚钱！\N{\rEng}because he always made money for his partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:23:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信\N{\rEng}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,超过30个职业乐师\N{\rEng}out of thirty professional musicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,队伍里竟没有一个意大利人\N{\rEng}there isn't one Italian in, in the group here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，我们来一曲塔兰泰拉\N{\rEng}Come on, let's have a tarantella!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你，起来！快，起来\N{\rEng}You! Up! Clarinet up, up, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.95,0:24:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这只手{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Questa mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.80,0:24:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这只手{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Questa mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.53,0:24:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊…\N{\rEng}What the hell have we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.34,0:24:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我见我妹妹一个人\N{\rEng}I'll see my sister alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.95,0:24:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那和我也有关 我留下来可以吗？\N{\rEng}It concerns me too. Is it okay if I stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.18,0:24:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗，亲爱的？\N{\rEng}How are you, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.74,0:24:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过梅尔，他在维加斯跟我在一起\N{\rEng}You've met Merle, he was with me in Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.68,0:25:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过他和你一起\N{\rEng}I saw him with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.54,0:25:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能给我一杯酒吗？\N{\rEng}Could I have a drink or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.11,0:25:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Que voi?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.17,0:25:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔，请你给他杯酒好吗？\N{\rEng}Al, would you please get him a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.58,0:25:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下周要去欧洲\N{\rEng}We're going to Europe next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.98,0:25:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在皇后号上订位\N{\rEng}I'd like to book passage on the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.80,0:25:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那你来找我干什么？\N{\rEng}So what do you come to me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.75,0:25:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛不去找旅行社呢？\N{\rEng}Why don't you go to a travel agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.80,0:25:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先要结婚\N{\rEng}We're getting married first.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.35,0:25:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你离婚证书上墨迹未干\N{\rEng}The ink on your divorce isn't dry yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.52,0:25:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你又要结婚了？\N{\rEng}and you're getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.76,0:25:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你周末去看你的孩子\N{\rEng}You see your children on weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.64,0:25:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你的长子维克托 在雷诺因小偷小摸被捕\N{\rEng}You know your oldest boy, Victor, was picked up in Reno for some petty theft
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.19,0:25:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你甚至不知道这件事 - 迈克尔\N{\rEng}- that you don't even know about. - Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.73,0:25:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟男人世界各地到处飞，他们根本不在乎你\N{\rEng}You fly around the world with men who don't even care for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.03,0:25:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 利用妓女一样利用你 - 你不是我父亲！\N{\rEng}- and use you like a whore! - You're not my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.27,0:25:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你来找我干什么？\N{\rEng}Then what do you come to me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.67,0:25:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我需要钱！\N{\rEng}'Cause I need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.31,0:26:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,康妮、康妮、康妮…\N{\rEng}Connie, Connie, Connie...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.71,0:26:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟你讲道理\N{\rEng}I wanna be reasonable with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.32,0:26:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何不跟我们待在一起，和家族在一起？\N{\rEng}Why don't you stay with us, with the family?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.24,0:26:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以居住在这处产业，和你的孩子在一起\N{\rEng}You can live on the estate with your kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.16,0:26:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会缺乏任何东西\N{\rEng}You won't be deprived of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.69,0:26:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以拥有任何你想要的东西\N{\rEng}and you can have everything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.12,0:26:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认识这位梅尔\N{\rEng}I don't know this Merle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.46,0:26:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他是干什么的 不知道他靠什么维生\N{\rEng}I don't know what he does. I don't know what he lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.15,0:26:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要不你告诉他结婚是不可能的\N{\rEng}Now why don't you tell him marriage is out of the question
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.32,0:26:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你不想再见到他\N{\rEng}and you don't want to see him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.54,0:26:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他会了解的 相信我\N{\rEng}He'll understand, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.73,0:26:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,康妮\N{\rEng}Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.71,0:26:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你不听我的\N{\rEng}If you don't listen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.24,0:27:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁给这个男人\N{\rEng}and marry this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.33,0:27:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你会令我很失望\N{\rEng}...you'll disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.33,0:27:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,家庭{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Famiglia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.73,0:27:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,百年{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Cent' anni
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.00,0:27:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“仙丹”是什么？\N{\rEng}What's "Chen dannay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.19,0:27:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“Cent' anni”意思是一百年！\N{\rEng}"Cent' anni". It means 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.53,0:27:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是我们都将 快乐的活一百年\N{\rEng}It means we should all live happily for 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.32,0:27:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,整个家族\N{\rEng}The family.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.83,0:27:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我父亲还活着那就是事实了\N{\rEng}That'd be true if my father were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.73,0:27:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,康妮\N{\rEng}Connie!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.31,0:28:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,梅尔\N{\rEng}Merle!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.44,0:28:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过我的嫂嫂蒂安娜了\N{\rEng}you've met my sister-in-law Deanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.37,0:28:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗雷多的妻子 - 我很荣幸\N{\rEng}- Fredo's wife. - My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.97,0:28:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 梅尔 - 我很荣幸\N{\rEng}- How do you do. - Merle - My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.22,0:28:10.19,Chs,,0,0,0,,- 他俩倒是挺配的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r} - 妈妈……{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.42,0:28:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她那是什么意思？\N{\rEng}What did she mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.20,0:28:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,请恕我直言{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}With all respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.42,0:28:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是来这吃晚饭的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I didn't come here to eat dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.80,0:28:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道…{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.53,0:28:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？我只是想跳舞而已\N{\rEng}What's the matter? I just, I just want to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.20,0:28:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,跳舞是跳舞，你已经东倒西歪了\N{\rEng}Dancing is one thing, you're fallin' all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.70,0:29:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是怎么回事\N{\rEng}I know what's the matter with you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.40,0:29:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你在吃醋 因为他才是真正的男子汉\N{\rEng}You're just jealous because he's a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.70,0:29:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我对天发誓，蒂安娜，我会当众抽你的\N{\rEng}I swear to God, Deanna, I'm gonna belt you right in the teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.22,0:29:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你连你妈都打不过\N{\rEng}You couldn't belt your mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.06,0:29:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗？\N{\rEng}You know somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.94,0:29:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那些意大利人，一碰到跟老婆有关的事就疯了\N{\rEng}These Dagos are crazy when it comes to their wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.10,0:29:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔说 如果你不能处理这件事\N{\rEng}Michael says that if you can't take care of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.23,0:29:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就得我来\N{\rEng}I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.47,0:29:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你去会好一点\N{\rEng}Maybe you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.13,0:29:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别嫁给意大利人\N{\rEng}Never marry a Wop.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.61,0:29:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对待自己老婆像狗屎一样\N{\rEng}They treat their wives like shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.61,0:29:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是有意说意大利人…\N{\rEng}I didn't mean to say Wop.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.13,0:29:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，噢，洛可，噢…\N{\rEng}Ahh, Ahh woo! Rocco! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.94,0:29:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？你这个大笨蛋！\N{\rEng}What are you doing to me, you big slob?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.64,0:29:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,救命！弗雷多！\N{\rEng}Help! Fredo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.36,0:29:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我控制不了她，麦基\N{\rEng}I can't control her, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.07,0:29:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我哥哥 弗雷多\N{\rEng}You're my brother, Fredo
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.10,0:29:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必对我道歉\N{\rEng}you don't have to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.07,0:29:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,克里门萨答应过罗萨托兄弟…\N{\rEng}Clemenza promised the Rosato brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.84,0:29:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他死后给他们三块布朗克斯的地盘\N{\rEng}three territories in the Bronx after he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.48,0:29:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你接管之后 并没有交给他们\N{\rEng}You took over and didn't give it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.07,0:29:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不履行约定？ - 你没履行\N{\rEng}- I welched? - You welched.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.26,0:29:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，克里门萨答应他们狗屁{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Yeah. Clemenza promised them lu cazzo,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.46,0:29:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,克里门萨没有承诺给他们什么\N{\rEng}Clemenza promised them nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.33,0:29:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他比我还要恨那些王八蛋\N{\rEng}He hated those son of a bitches more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.00,0:29:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基，他们感觉受骗了\N{\rEng}Frankie, they feel cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.35,0:29:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\rEng}Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你高坐在内华达雪乐山上\N{\rEng}You're sitting up in the Sierra Mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.71,0:30:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝着…他喝的是什么？\N{\rEng}and you're drinking...What's he drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.81,0:30:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,香槟\N{\rEng}Champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.82,0:30:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,香槟 香槟鸡尾酒\N{\rEng}Champagne...Champagne cocktails
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.00,0:30:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要对我如何经管自己的家族下判决\N{\rEng}and you're passing judgement on how I run my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.63,0:30:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家族 依然叫柯利昂尼{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Your family's still called Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.80,0:30:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你要管理的像柯利昂尼家族{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}And you'll run it like a Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.73,0:30:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的家族不吃这里的，也不吃拉斯维加斯的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}My family doesn't eat here, doesn't eat in Las Vegas...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.08,0:30:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,更不吃迈阿密的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}…\N{\rEng}...and doesn't eat in Miami...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.84,0:30:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的海门·罗斯{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}...with Hyman Roth!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.17,0:30:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基\N{\rEng}Franki
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.17,0:30:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个老好人，我也喜欢你\N{\rEng}You're a good old man, and I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.96,0:30:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多年来你一直对我父亲忠诚\N{\rEng}You were loyal to my father for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.80,0:30:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,罗萨托兄弟在抓人质\N{\rEng}The Rosato brothers are taking hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.90,0:30:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还有，麦克，他们口水直接吐在我脸上\N{\rEng}And Mike, they spit right in my face,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.59,0:30:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,全因为他们有迈阿密那个犹太人撑腰\N{\rEng}all because they're backed up by that Jew in Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.06,0:30:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.65,0:30:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才不要碰他们\N{\rEng}That's why I don't want them touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.20,0:30:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不要碰他们？ - 不要！\N{\rEng}- You don't wanna them touched? - No
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.80,0:31:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你对他们公平\N{\rEng}I want you to be fair with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.96,0:31:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我对他们公平？\N{\rEng}You want me to be fair with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.75,0:31:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆，你怎么能对禽兽公平？\N{\rEng}Tom, how can you be fair to animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.31,0:31:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆，老天在上，听我说\N{\rEng}Tom, for Chris sakes. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.86,0:31:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们招募西班牙人，他们招募黑鬼\N{\rEng}They recruit spics, they recruit niggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.50,0:31:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在他们祖母的街坊中使用暴力\N{\rEng}You know, they do violence in their grandmothers' neighbourhoods!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.50,0:31:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我告诉你，跟他们混在一起的就是妓女\N{\rEng}And I tell you, everything with them is whores!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.40,0:31:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妓女！还有垃圾，毒品！\N{\rEng}Whores! And junk, dope!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.94,0:31:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还把赌博放在最后\N{\rEng}And they leave the gambling to last.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.63,0:31:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我要经营自己的家族\N{\rEng}I want to run my family
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.97,0:31:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要你在背后\N{\rEng}without you on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.75,0:31:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而且我要罗萨托兄弟去死 - 不行\N{\rEng}- and I want those Rosato brothers dead! - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,死{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Mort'
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.40,0:31:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我和海门·罗斯 有重要的生意要做\N{\rEng}Now I have business that's important with Hyman Roth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.61,0:31:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要被干扰\N{\rEng}I don't want it disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.96,0:31:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是把对一个犹太人的忠诚 放在自己的血族之前\N{\rEng}Then you give your loyalty to a Jew before your own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.41,0:31:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样，弗兰基\N{\rEng}Come on, Frankie,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.37,0:31:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我父亲和海门·罗斯 做过生意\N{\rEng}You know my father did business with Hyman Roth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.18,0:31:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他尊重他\N{\rEng}He respected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.72,0:32:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲和海门·罗斯做过生意\N{\rEng}Your father did business with Hyman Roth,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.14,0:32:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲尊重海门·罗斯\N{\rEng}Your father respected Hyman Roth,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.83,0:32:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但你父亲从未信任过海门·罗斯\N{\rEng}but your father never trusted Hyman Roth
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.61,0:32:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,或他的西西里人信差 约翰尼·欧拉\N{\rEng}or his Sicilian messenger boy Johnny Ola.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.53,0:32:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须原谅我告退{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You'll have to excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.83,0:32:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我累了，又有点醉了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I'm tired, and I'm a little drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.86,0:32:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我要这的每一位都知道\N{\rEng}I want everybody here to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.46,0:32:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会为各位添任何的麻烦\N{\rEng}there's not going to be no trouble from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.50,0:32:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·柯利昂尼\N{\rEng}Don Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.60,0:32:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奇齐 开门{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Cicci, the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.80,0:32:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你要他现在离开吗？\N{\rEng}You want him to leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.45,0:32:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,让他回纽约去吧\N{\rEng}Let him go back to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.24,0:32:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经拟好我的计划了\N{\rEng}I've already made my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.85,0:32:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那老头喝太多酒了\N{\rEng}The old man had too much wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.80,0:32:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,挺晚了\N{\rEng}It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.75,0:33:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,胎儿怎么样？\N{\rEng}How's the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.90,0:33:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在我肚子里睡着\N{\rEng}Sleeping inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.92,0:33:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉是个男孩吗？\N{\rEng}Does it feel like a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.53,0:33:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是个男孩 麦克\N{\rEng}Yes, it does, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.95,0:33:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊\N{\rEng}Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.86,0:33:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉今天这么多人\N{\rEng}I'm sorry about all the people today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.62,0:33:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,时机不好，但是我也无能为力\N{\rEng}Bad timing. It couldn't be helped, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.74,0:33:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这令我想起你有一次告诉过我\N{\rEng}It made me think of what you once told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.84,0:33:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,“5年之内柯利昂尼家族会完全合法化”\N{\rEng}"In five years the Corleone family will be completely legitimate."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.50,0:33:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那是7年前了\N{\rEng}That was seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.63,0:33:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.83,0:33:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我在努力，亲爱的\N{\rEng}I'm trying, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.30,0:34:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过这个了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.70,0:35:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，窗帘为什么开着？\N{\rEng}Michael, why are the drapes open?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.62,0:35:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 凯伊，你还好吗？ - 还好\N{\rEng}- Kay, are you all right? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.74,0:35:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你有没有中弹? - 没有\N{\rEng}- Are you hit? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.14,0:35:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,过去了 过去了\N{\rEng}It's over It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.29,0:35:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,把门关起来！\N{\rEng}Get the door locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.90,0:35:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,停住 停住\N{\rEng}Halt, halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.67,0:36:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还在园子里\N{\rEng}They're still on the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.30,0:36:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托，麦克，拜托你留在里面\N{\rEng}Please, Michael, please stay inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.74,0:36:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要活口\N{\rEng}Keep them alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.77,0:36:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们尽力 - 洛可，要活的\N{\rEng}- We'll try. - Rocco, alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.51,0:36:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,留在门口\N{\rEng}Stay by the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.40,0:36:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,留在房子周围\N{\rEng}Stay around house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.91,0:37:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\rEng}Yeah, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.00,0:37:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,麦基，你还好吗？\N{\rEng}Mikey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.50,0:37:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事 - 没事？\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.33,0:37:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有许多事我不能告诉你，汤姆\N{\rEng}There's a lot I can't tell you, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.73,0:37:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道过去你因此而心烦\N{\rEng}and I now that's upset you in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.83,0:37:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是有点儿 - 是的…\N{\rEng}- A little. - Yeah, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.40,0:38:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得那是因为缺乏信任或信心\N{\rEng}You felt it was because of some lack of trust or confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.70,0:38:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是…\N{\rEng}But it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.20,0:38:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我钦佩你，而且我爱你\N{\rEng}it's because I admire you and I love you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.71,0:38:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才把事情对你保守秘密\N{\rEng}that I kept things secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.12,0:38:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在这个时刻，你是我唯一能完全信任的人\N{\rEng}It's why at this moment you're the only one I can completely trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.01,0:38:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多？\N{\rEng}Fredo?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.00,0:38:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他心地善良\N{\rEng}Well, he's got a good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.73,0:38:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他懦弱，而且他愚蠢\N{\rEng}But he's weak and he's stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.10,0:38:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而这是生死攸关的事\N{\rEng}And this is life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.10,0:38:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆\N{\rEng}Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.94,0:38:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的兄弟\N{\rEng}you're my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.05,0:38:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想你把我看作兄弟，麦基\N{\rEng}I always wanted to be thought of as a brother by you, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.71,0:38:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的兄弟\N{\rEng}A real brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.72,0:38:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这我知道\N{\rEng}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.72,0:38:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你要来接手\N{\rEng}You're going to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.10,0:38:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你要成为唐\N{\rEng}You're going to be the Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.23,0:39:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我认为要发生的事情已经发生了\N{\rEng}If what I think is happen has happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.64,0:39:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚就要离开这里\N{\rEng}I'm leaving here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.66,0:39:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我给予你一个唐完全的权力\N{\rEng}I give you complete power of a Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.62,0:39:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,囊括弗雷多和他的人\N{\rEng}Over Fredo and his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.13,0:39:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,洛可，奈利，所有人\N{\rEng}Rocco, Neri, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.34,0:39:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我把我妻子的性命交付给你\N{\rEng}I'm trusting you with the lives of my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.96,0:39:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我的孩子们\N{\rEng}and my children,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.83,0:39:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这个家族的未来\N{\rEng}the future of this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.60,0:39:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们抓到这些傢伙\N{\rEng}If we catch these guys
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.94,0:39:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你看有否可能查出 幕后主使者吗？\N{\rEng}do you think we'll be able to find out who's back on...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.06,0:39:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要去抓\N{\rEng}We won't catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.50,0:39:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我完全错了，他们已经死了\N{\rEng}Unless I'm very wrong, they're dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.47,0:39:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,被一位跟我们很亲近的人杀死\N{\rEng}They were killed by somebody close to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.61,0:39:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,内奸\N{\rEng}Inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.35,0:39:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,非常非常害怕他们搞砸了\N{\rEng}Very, very frightened that they botched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.96,0:39:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你的人呢？洛可和奈利\N{\rEng}Well, but your peaople, Rocco and Neri
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.75,0:39:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会认为他们与此事有关吧？\N{\rEng}You don't think they had something to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.57,0:39:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你看…\N{\rEng}You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.16,0:39:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的人都是生意人\N{\rEng}All our people are businessmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.53,0:40:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的忠诚以此为基础\N{\rEng}Their loyalty is based on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.85,0:40:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有一件事 我从爸爸那里学来的\N{\rEng}One thing I learned from Pop...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.93,0:40:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是试着像你身边的人那样去思考\N{\rEng}...was to try to think as people around you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.45,0:40:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个基础上 凡事都有可能\N{\rEng}On that basis, anything is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.26,0:40:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，他们死了\N{\rEng}Mike, they're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.36,0:40:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我窗户上\N{\rEng}Right on my window!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.20,0:40:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要离开这里 他们躺在那里死了\N{\rEng}I want to get out of here. They're lying there dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.60,0:40:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拉她进去！\N{\rEng}Get her in!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.48,0:40:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在这边 他们有两个人\N{\rEng}Over here! There's two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.57,0:40:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看来他们是纽约以外的人雇的\N{\rEng}Looks like they were hired out of New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.57,0:40:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认识他们\N{\rEng}I don't recognise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.20,0:40:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在问不出什么了\N{\rEng}Won't get anything out of them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.70,0:40:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看，看…\N{\rEng}Look, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.30,0:40:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们解决掉\N{\rEng}Fish them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.80,0:41:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，把尸体料理掉\N{\rEng}All righ, get rid of the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.42,0:41:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克到哪去了？\N{\rEng}Where's Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.53,0:41:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,洛可\N{\rEng}Rocco.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.08,0:41:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼\N{\rEng}Anthony
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.90,0:41:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好的，去睡吧！\N{\rEng}everything is going to be all right. Try to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.60,0:42:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢你的派对吗？\N{\rEng}Did you like your party?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.55,0:42:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我收到很多礼物 - 我知道\N{\rEng}- I got lots of presents. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.60,0:42:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢它们吗？\N{\rEng}Did you like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.63,0:42:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我不认识送我礼物的那些人\N{\rEng}Yeah. I didn't know the people who gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.70,0:42:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，他们都是朋友\N{\rEng}Well, they were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.53,0:42:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到我送你的礼物了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you see my present for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.66,0:42:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就放在我的枕头上\N{\rEng}It was on my pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.33,0:42:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼\N{\rEng}Anthony.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.23,0:42:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天一大早就要离开\N{\rEng}I'm going to be leaving very early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.25,0:42:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你会带我去吗？ - 不，不行，安东尼\N{\rEng}- Will you take me? - No, I can't, Anthony.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.72,0:42:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么必须要去？\N{\rEng}Why do you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.71,0:42:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须去做生意\N{\rEng}I have to do business.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.27,0:42:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮你忙\N{\rEng}I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.10,0:42:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，有一天你会的\N{\rEng}I know. Some day you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.20,0:43:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,睡一会儿吧！\N{\rEng}Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.68,0:44:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她真漂亮，你必须见见她{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}She's really beautiful.You've got to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.43,0:44:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你等着看她吧，言语无法形容她的美{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Wait till you see her. Words can't describe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.90,0:45:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我离开了那不勒斯，离开了妈妈{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I left Naples. I left Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.07,0:45:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为了辛苦的漂泊{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}For a no-good tramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.06,0:45:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我来到美国，来到纽约{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Now here I am in America, in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.58,0:45:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,独自一人 想念我的妈妈{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Alone! Thinking of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.30,0:45:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没有家中的消息{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Without news from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.80,0:45:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,进来{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.52,0:45:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,佩皮诺，有你的信{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Pepino, a letter for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.52,0:45:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.23,0:45:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,终于，那不勒斯来信了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Finally, a letter from Naples!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.72,0:45:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，维多，喜欢我的小天使吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Vito, how do you like my little angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.42,0:45:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她漂亮吧？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Isn't she beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.42,0:45:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她是很美{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}She's very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.45,0:45:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮，对吧？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Beautiful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.00,0:45:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对你而言，她很美{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}To you, she's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.42,0:45:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对我，只有我的妻子和儿子{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}For me, there's only my wife and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.59,0:45:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的妈妈{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}And mama
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.10,0:45:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈死了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Our dear mother is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.20,0:45:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Mama
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.30,0:45:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Mama
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.20,0:45:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈咪呀{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Mamamia
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.10,0:46:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等会到后台去 带她去吃饭{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}We'll go backstage later and take her to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.50,0:46:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，坐下，笨蛋{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Sit down, you bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.50,0:46:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}you bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.73,0:47:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，唐·法努奇{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Oh, excuse me, Don Fanucci.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.97,0:47:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到后台去看她{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}We'll go see her backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.56,0:47:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.07,0:47:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,黑手党{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}The Black Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.82,0:47:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,维多，赶紧，我们走{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Vito, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.42,0:47:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 我们到后台去看她\N{\rEng}Come on let's go see her backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.83,0:47:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,借过…借过{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Sorry, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.61,0:47:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这边走\N{\rEng}Come her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.96,0:47:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是法努奇，那个黑手党{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}That's Fanucci... the Black Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.97,0:48:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明天再说吧{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}We'll talk about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.93,0:48:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明天，明天，永远是明天{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Tomorrow! Always tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.13,0:48:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天就要付钱{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You'll pay me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.20,0:48:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.00,0:48:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快付钱{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r} - 别弄我女儿，放开她{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}- Pay me now! - Not my daughter! Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.81,0:48:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,给，我所有的钱都给你{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Here, take all my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.97,0:48:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,维多…走吧\N{\rEng}Vito, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.97,0:48:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你怎么想{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I know what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.64,0:48:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但事情不是那样的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}But you don't know how things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.74,0:48:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,法努奇是黑手党{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Fanucci's with the Black Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.37,0:48:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这整个街区都给他交钱{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}The whole neighborhood pays him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.81,0:48:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是我开杂货店的爸爸{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Even my father, in the grocery store.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.90,0:48:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他是意大利人吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Is he Italian...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.44,0:48:58.75,Chs,,0,0,0,,他是的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.20,0:49:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他为何要骚扰其他意大利人？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}...why does he bother other Italians?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.80,0:49:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道没别人保护他们\N{\rEng}He knows they have nobody to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.08,0:49:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别管那个 喜欢我的小天使吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Forget that. Did you like my angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.65,0:49:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你高兴，我就高兴{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}If you're happy, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.65,0:49:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,工作顺利吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Don't you feel well?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.67,0:50:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你老板对你还好吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Is your boss treating you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.43,0:50:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别提它了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.91,0:50:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，老乡{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Hey! Paisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.75,0:50:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你会说意大利语吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You speak Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.85,0:50:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我藏一下，下星期我再回来拿{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Hide this for me! Next week. I'll come and get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.85,0:51:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,阿班丹多 见过我的侄子{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Abbandando, meet my nephew!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.61,0:51:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,生意好吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}How's business?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.58,0:51:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 很好{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}It's good, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.48,0:51:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,法努奇疯了! 说邻居在拖付钱的限期{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Fanucci's mad. Says the neighborhood's getting sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.56,0:51:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,说人们不准时付钱 不付全额的钱{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}People don't pay on time, don't pay the full amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.23,0:51:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,说他对大家都太好了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Says he's been too nice to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.96,0:51:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以法努奇要改变了？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}So Fanucci's changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.33,0:51:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 他想收双倍的钱{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Sure. He wants double from everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.96,0:52:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,连我父亲也是{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Even from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.57,0:52:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的朋友 对不对？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I'm a friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.64,0:52:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你要让他在这里做事{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}So you'll let him work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.21,0:52:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,维多，过来一下{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Vito,come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.60,0:52:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,维多，我有一个坏消息{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I've got some bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.96,0:52:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得很惭愧告诉你这个…{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I feel rotten about telling you this...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.95,0:52:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但法努奇…{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}But Fanucci...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.02,0:52:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他有个侄子 而你必须把我的工作给他{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}he's got a nephew...And you have to give him my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.23,0:53:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你从我来这起 就一直对我很好{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You've always been good to me, ever since I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.03,0:53:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你像父亲般照顾我{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You looked after me like a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.05,0:53:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我谢谢你 而且我不会忘记{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I thank you.And I won't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.86,0:53:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,维多{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Vito!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.94,0:53:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\rEng}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.44,0:53:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.70,0:53:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个带回去{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Take this to your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.65,0:53:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 但是我不能接受{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Thanks anyway. But please, I can't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.01,0:53:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给你的家人{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r} - 我不能接受{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}- Take this to your family. - I can't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.53,0:53:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.06,0:54:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的梨子{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}What a nice pear!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.28,0:54:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是克里门萨 我的货还在你那？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I'm Clemenza, you still have my goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.03,0:54:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有看过里面？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Did you look inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.72,0:54:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我对与我无关的东西没兴趣{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I'm not interested in things that don't concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.83,0:55:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个朋友有张很好的地毯{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}A friend of mine has a nice rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.43,0:55:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你妻子会喜欢{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Maybe your wife would like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.07,0:55:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她当然会，但谁有钱买地毯啊？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Sure she would. But who has money for a rug?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.85,0:55:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是件礼物，我知道怎样报答别人帮忙{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}It would be a present. I know how to return a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.75,0:55:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,当然好，我妻子会喜欢它的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Yeah,sure. My wife would like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.64,0:55:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们走{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.83,0:56:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个王八蛋 他不在家{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}The son of a bitch! He isn't home!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.06,0:56:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,该死，连钥匙都没留下{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Damn, he didn't even leave the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.15,0:56:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会介意的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Well, he won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.43,0:56:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\rEng}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.93,0:56:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，维多，进来吧\N{\rEng}Hey, Vito, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.97,0:56:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心，进来吧{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Please come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.27,0:57:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是你朋友的地方？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r} - 是的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}- This is your friend's place? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.90,0:57:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真像一座宫殿{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}This is a real palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.30,0:57:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的一座{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}One of the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.57,0:57:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,维多，帮帮手，好吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Vito, give me a hand, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.44,0:59:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看看多漂亮，桑提诺{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Look how pretty it is, Santino!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.94,1:01:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\rEng}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.68,1:01:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系，来吧\N{\rEng}It's all right. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.41,1:01:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,海门在里面\N{\rEng}Hyman's in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.67,1:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在弄午餐，你要来一个鲔鱼三明治吗？\N{\rEng}I just making some lunch. Would you like a tuna sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.71,1:01:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不了，谢谢你\N{\rEng}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.76,1:02:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯先生？\N{\rEng}Mr. Roth?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.83,1:02:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,进来，迈克尔\N{\rEng}Come in, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.24,1:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧，随意些\N{\rEng}Sit down, make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.69,1:02:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,快结束了\N{\rEng}It's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.77,1:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你追美式足球赛吗？\N{\rEng}Do you follow the football game?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.17,1:02:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有一阵子没看了\N{\rEng}Not for a while I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.14,1:02:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢在下午看足球赛\N{\rEng}I enjoy watching football in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.17,1:02:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜爱这国家的几样事情之一\N{\rEng}One of the things I love about this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.04,1:02:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,棒球也是\N{\rEng}Baseball too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.28,1:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜爱棒球，从阿诺德·罗斯坦操纵1919年职棒世界大赛开始\N{\rEng}I love bassball, ever since Arnold Rothstein fixed the World Series in 1919.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.18,1:02:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你有些麻烦\N{\rEng}I heard you had some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.41,1:02:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢\N{\rEng}Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.31,1:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,人们拿枪做出那种行为\N{\rEng}People behaving like that with guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.22,1:03:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是你没事\N{\rEng}The important thing is you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.12,1:03:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,健康是最重要的事！\N{\rEng}Good health is the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.12,1:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,超过成功，超过金钱\N{\rEng}More than success, more than money.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.66,1:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,超过权力\N{\rEng}More than power.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.80,1:03:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这是因为 将会有更多流血事件\N{\rEng}I came here because there's going to be more bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.77,1:03:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要你在发生之前有所了解\N{\rEng}I wanted you to know before it happens
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.90,1:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就没有引发另一场战争的危险\N{\rEng}so there's no dangerous starting another war.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.80,1:03:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人想要另一场战争\N{\rEng}Nobody wants another war.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.87,1:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克·潘坦吉利到我家里来\N{\rEng}Frank Pentangeli came to my home
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.37,1:03:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他请求我准许除掉罗萨托兄弟\N{\rEng}and asked my permission to get rid of the Rosato brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.81,1:03:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当我拒绝时，他试图派人杀我\N{\rEng}When I refused he tried to have me killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.23,1:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他很笨，我运气好\N{\rEng}He was stupid, I was lucky.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.87,1:03:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快会去拜访他\N{\rEng}I'll visit him soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.75,1:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是，什么也不能妨碍我们的未来计划\N{\rEng}The important thing is that nothing interferes with our plans for the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.91,1:04:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的和我的 - 没有什么比那更重要\N{\rEng}- Yours and mine. - Nothing is more important.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.15,1:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个聪明并考虑周到的年轻人\N{\rEng}You're a wise and considerate young man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.21,1:04:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而你是位伟人，罗斯先生\N{\rEng}And you're a great man, Mr. Roth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.18,1:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要向你学习很多\N{\rEng}There's much I can learn from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.82,1:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮上忙的都行，迈克尔\N{\rEng}Whatever I can do to help, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.32,1:04:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打扰了，午餐 - 进来\N{\rEng}- Excuse me. Lunch. - Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.20,1:04:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 亲爱的\N{\rEng}Thank you, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.05,1:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你这干什么？会震破耳膜的\N{\rEng}What're you doing? You're going to break your eardrums.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.96,1:04:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了，慢用 - 谢谢你\N{\rEng}- Okay, enjoy it. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.17,1:04:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你年轻，我老了，还有病\N{\rEng}You're young, I'm old and sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.14,1:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在接下来几个月一起要做的事…\N{\rEng}What we'll do together in the next few months...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.10,1:04:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,将创造历史，迈克尔\N{\rEng}will make history, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.20,1:04:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,历史，那是从未有过的事\N{\rEng}Histery. It's never been done before.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.01,1:04:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,连你父亲都没有梦想过这种事情会有可能\N{\rEng}Not even your father would dream that such a thing could be possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.70,1:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那么潘坦吉利死定了\N{\rEng}Then Frank Pentangeli is a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.60,1:04:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不反对吧？\N{\rEng}You don't object?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.68,1:05:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是个小角色！\N{\rEng}He's small potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.48,1:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\rEng}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.22,1:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有客人吗？\N{\rEng}We got company?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.58,1:05:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.90,1:05:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔·柯利昂尼来了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Michael Corleone is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.52,1:05:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，迈克尔·柯利昂尼？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Oh, Michael Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.61,1:05:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪里？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Where's he?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.61,1:05:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他在你的房里，你最好快点{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}He's in your den. You better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.74,1:05:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他等了半个小时了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}He's been waiting a half hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.93,1:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不对吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.06,1:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·柯利昂尼\N{\rEng}Don Corleone
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.25,1:06:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你早告诉你你要来\N{\rEng}I wish you would have let me know you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.42,1:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好让我为你准备些东西\N{\rEng}I could have prepared something for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.85,1:06:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让你知道我要来\N{\rEng}I didn't want you to know I was coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.12,1:06:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说我家发生的事了吗？\N{\rEng}You heard what happened in my home?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.00,1:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克 我差点没吓死\N{\rEng}Mike, I almost died myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.42,1:06:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们都松了口气… - 在我家里\N{\rEng}- We were all so relieved... - In my home!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.12,1:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的卧室，我妻子睡觉的地方\N{\rEng}In my bedroom where my wife sleeps!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.86,1:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子进来玩玩具的地方\N{\rEng}Where my children come in play with they toys.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.96,1:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在我家里\N{\rEng}In my home.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.04,1:06:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你帮助我报复\N{\rEng}I want you to help me take my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.10,1:06:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，什么都行\N{\rEng}Michael, anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.35,1:06:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做什么？\N{\rEng}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.98,1:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,摆平跟罗萨托兄弟的麻烦\N{\rEng}Settle these troubles with the Rosato brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.31,1:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，我不明白\N{\rEng}Mike, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.08,1:07:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不…你看，我没有你那种脑筋\N{\rEng}I don't...Look, I don't have your brain
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.95,1:07:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去做大生意\N{\rEng}for big deals.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.32,1:07:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是街头斗争\N{\rEng}But this is a street thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.96,1:07:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个迈阿密的海门·罗斯，那个…\N{\rEng}That Hyman Roth in Miami. That...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.92,1:07:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他在支持那些王八蛋\N{\rEng} He's backing up those sons-of-bitches.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.12,1:07:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他在支持\N{\rEng}I know he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.29,1:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么？为什么你要我跟他们休兵，麦克？\N{\rEng}Then why? Why did you ask me to lay down to them, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.70,1:07:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是海门·罗斯试图派人杀我\N{\rEng}It was Hyman Roth that tried to have me killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.87,1:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是他\N{\rEng}I know it was him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.07,1:07:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷，麦克\N{\rEng}Jesus Christ, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.70,1:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老天，来，让我们把他们全干掉！\N{\rEng}Jesus Christ, look, let's get them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.55,1:07:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把他们全干掉！\N{\rEng}Let's get 'em all.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.67,1:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就现在，趁我们还有力量\N{\rEng}Now while we've got the muscle.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.67,1:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这里曾是我父亲的旧书房\N{\rEng}This used to be my father's old study.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.55,1:07:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,现在变了\N{\rEng}It's changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.88,1:07:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得以前有…\N{\rEng}I remember there used to be a...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.41,1:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一张大书桌在这里\N{\rEng}a big desk here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.28,1:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得我还是孩子时，弗兰基\N{\rEng}I remember when I was a kid, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.14,1:08:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这附近玩必须很小声\N{\rEng}We had to be quiet when we played near here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.93,1:08:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴这幢房子从没落入陌生人的手里\N{\rEng}I was very happy that this house never went to strangers.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.96,1:08:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,先是克里门萨接手 现在是你\N{\rEng}First Clemenza took it over. Now you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.63,1:08:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲在这里教了我许多事情\N{\rEng}My father taught me many things here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.53,1:08:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这房间里教我\N{\rEng}He taught me in this room.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.13,1:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他教我…\N{\rEng}He taught me...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.75,1:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“与你的朋友保持亲近\N{\rEng}"Keep your friends close,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.95,1:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,“但与你的敌人要更亲近”\N{\rEng}but your enemies closer."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.37,1:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现在如果海门·罗斯看到我协调此事\N{\rEng}If Hyman Roth sees that I interceded in this thing
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.01,1:08:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在帮衬罗萨托兄弟\N{\rEng}in the Rosato brothers' favour
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.74,1:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他会认为他跟我的关系依然良好\N{\rEng}he's gonna think his relationship with me is still good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.58,1:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r} - 明白{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}- Capide? - Capide.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.06,1:08:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是要他那样想\N{\rEng}That's what I want him to think.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.20,1:08:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要他们彻底放松\N{\rEng}I want him completely relaxed
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.12,1:09:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们的友谊有绝对的信心\N{\rEng}and confident in our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.10,1:09:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就能查出我家族里的叛徒是谁\N{\rEng}Then I'll be able to find out who the traitor in my family was.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.53,1:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rEng}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.90,1:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多，我是约翰尼\N{\rEng}Fredo, this is Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.81,1:09:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰尼·欧拉，我们需要更多协助\N{\rEng}Johnny Ola. We need some more help.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.42,1:09:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰尼？\N{\rEng}Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.37,1:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷，这是什么鬼时候了？\N{\rEng}Jesus Christ, what the hell time is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.70,1:09:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁啊，亲？\N{\rEng}Who's that, honey?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.08,1:09:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了，弗雷多\N{\rEng}Listen good, Fredo,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.70,1:09:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你打到这里找我干嘛？\N{\rEng}Why are you calling me here for?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.38,1:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想跟你谈\N{\rEng}I don't want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.93,1:09:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,潘坦吉利定下跟罗萨托兄弟会面\N{\rEng}Pentangeli setup a meeting with the Rosato brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.21,1:09:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他要接受那个协定\N{\rEng}He said he's gonna go for that deal
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.55,1:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEng}Oh, god
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.77,1:09:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他会一个人来吗？  - 我什么都不知道\N{\rEng}- Will he come alone? - I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.24,1:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经让我陷得够深了\N{\rEng}You've got me in deep enough already.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.89,1:10:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,继续下去\N{\rEng}Just go along,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.25,1:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会顺利的，弗雷多\N{\rEng}everything will be all right, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.85,1:10:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,潘坦吉利说他愿意达成协议\N{\rEng}Pentangeli says he's willing to make a deal
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.45,1:10:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只想知道他是否坦诚，还是会带手下一起来\N{\rEng}All we wanna know is if he's on the level, or if he'll bring his boys
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.99,1:10:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们对我说谎，我不要你再给我打电话\N{\rEng}You guys lied to me. I don't want you to call me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.16,1:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你弟弟不会发现我们谈过的\N{\rEng}Your brother's not gonna find out we talked
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.74,1:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\rEng}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.60,1:10:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁？\N{\rEng}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.80,1:10:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,打错了\N{\rEng}Wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.80,1:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基，我这里什么人都没带\N{\rEng}Frankie, I've got nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.67,1:10:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在车上等，奇齐\N{\rEng}Wait in the car, Cicc'.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.10,1:10:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗兰基 - 没事的，奇齐\N{\rEng}- Frankie. - That's okay, Cicc'.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.71,1:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\N{\rEng}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.12,1:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们新协议的幸运纸条\N{\rEng}A lucky C note for our new deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.76,1:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞奇 给我们倒杯酒\N{\rEng}Ritchie. Give us a taste.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.49,1:11:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对于你的决定都很高兴 弗兰克\N{\rEng}We were all real happy about your decision, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.61,1:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会后悔的\N{\rEng}You won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.65,1:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢这个纸条，罗萨托\N{\rEng}I don't like the C note, Rosato.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.08,1:11:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它当作是一种侮辱\N{\rEng}I take that as an insult.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.69,1:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔·柯利昂尼问好\N{\rEng}Michael Corleone says hello!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.25,1:11:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快点…快他妈的关门\N{\rEng}Come here...Close the fucking door!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.41,1:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你那个警察朋友，怎么…\N{\rEng}Your friend the cop. What the...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.90,1:11:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，瑞奇，里面很暗\N{\rEng}Hey, Ritch. It's dark in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.66,1:11:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是营业还是打烊了？\N{\rEng}Are you open or closed?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.25,1:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是进来稍微整理一下\N{\rEng}I just came in to clean up a little, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.26,1:11:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.90,1:11:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,地板上有东西吗？\N{\rEng}Is that something on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.22,1:12:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卡迈因，不，别在这里… - 安东尼！\N{\rEng}-Carmine, no, not here! -Anthony!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.22,1:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你打开酒吧门 我就把你的脑袋给轰掉\N{\rEng}You open the fucking bar and I'll blow your head off!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.10,1:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,卡迈因\N{\rEng}Carmine
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.72,1:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪，见到你真好\N{\rEng}Freddy, it's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.80,1:13:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样？\N{\rEng}How is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.80,1:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他没事，他在后面\N{\rEng}He's okay. He's in the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.06,1:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，姑娘们，闪到一边去\N{\rEng}Come on, girls, take a hike.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.83,1:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在这间房里面\N{\rEng}In this room here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.70,1:13:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要先跟他单独谈谈\N{\rEng}I want to talk to him alone first.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.33,1:13:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧的\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.78,1:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我能帮助你，参议员\N{\rEng}I thought I could help you, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.61,1:13:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,黑根？\N{\rEng}Hagen?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.82,1:13:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，黑根，我没有…\N{\rEng}Listen, Hagen, I did not...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.90,1:13:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不用，没事了\N{\rEng}No, It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.00,1:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没有做\N{\rEng}I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.18,1:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.42,1:13:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你很幸运\N{\rEng}You're very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.66,1:13:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟弟弗雷多管理这地方\N{\rEng}My brother Fredo operates this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.35,1:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他比其他人都早被告知\N{\rEng}He was called before anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.12,1:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这要是发生在别的地方 我们也帮不了你\N{\rEng}Had this happened some place else we couldn't have helped you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.22,1:14:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,当我醒来时 我在地板上\N{\rEng}When I woke up, I was on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.72,1:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我不知道那是怎么发生的\N{\rEng}And I don't know how it happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.90,1:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你记不起来了？\N{\rEng}You can't remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.36,1:14:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我昏过去了\N{\rEng}I passed out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.84,1:14:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我来整理！\N{\rEng}I...I picked!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.71,1:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个游戏\N{\rEng}Just a game.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.82,1:14:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\rEng}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.82,1:14:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 老天\N{\rEng}Jesus, Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.05,1:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,老天，老天\N{\rEng}Jesus, Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.42,1:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝…\N{\rEng}God!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.12,1:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，上帝…\N{\rEng}Oh God!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.05,1:15:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，而且我不懂为什么我记不起来\N{\rEng}I don't know, and I don't understand why I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.02,1:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必记得，只要照我说的做\N{\rEng}You don't have to remember it, just do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.16,1:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,打个电话到你的办公室去\N{\rEng}Put in a call to your office.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.62,1:15:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,解释一下\N{\rEng}Explain
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.75,1:15:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说你明天下午会到\N{\rEng}that you'll be there tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.60,1:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你决定在迈克尔·柯利昂尼家住一晚，在塔霍\N{\rEng}You decided to spend the night at Michael Corleone's house in Tahoe.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.54,1:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,作为他的客人\N{\rEng}As his guest.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.17,1:15:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的确记得她在笑\N{\rEng}I do remember that she was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.15,1:15:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们以前也玩过\N{\rEng}We'd done it before
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.10,1:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我不可能伤害那个女孩\N{\rEng}and I know that I could not have hurt that girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.70,1:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女孩没有家人\N{\rEng}This girl has no family.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.51,1:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人知道她在这里工作\N{\rEng}Nobody knows that she worked here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.13,1:15:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这会像是她从未存在过一样\N{\rEng}It'll be as though she never existed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.02,1:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的只是我们的友谊\N{\rEng}All that's left is our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.90,1:16:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\rEng}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.92,1:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，柯利昂尼太太，我们奉命不能让你过去\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, Mrs. Corleone, but we're not to let you through.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.50,1:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是要去市场\N{\rEng}I'm just going to the market.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.10,1:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，你只要把单子给我们\N{\rEng}Okay, you just give us the list.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.33,1:16:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你要什么我们给你买回来\N{\rEng}We'll pick up anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.87,1:16:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是谁的命令？\N{\rEng}Whose orders are these?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.20,1:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,黑根先生的，夫人，他现在过来了\N{\rEng}Mr. Hagen's, ma'am. He's coming over now.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.00,1:16:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，那我得和黑根先生谈谈\N{\rEng}All right. I want is to speak to Mr. Hagen.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.64,1:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我原先要跟你解释的，但我要在塔霍市办些事\N{\rEng}I wanted to explain, but I had business in Carson City.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.41,1:16:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是麦克的要求 为了你的安全\N{\rEng}Now, this is Michael's request for your safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.46,1:16:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以安排任何你需要的东西\N{\rEng}We can set up anything that you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.61,1:16:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了，我就该待在自己屋子里？\N{\rEng}I see. I'm supposed to stay in my house?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.31,1:16:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不，在园子里都可以\N{\rEng}No, within the compound will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.81,1:16:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆，我原打算下周带孩子们去新英格兰\N{\rEng}Tom, I was going to take children to New England next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.22,1:16:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那不行\N{\rEng}That's off.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.77,1:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个囚犯？是不是？\N{\rEng}Am I a prisoner? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.64,1:16:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不那么看，凯伊\N{\rEng}That's not how we see it, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.05,1:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.85,1:16:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，孩子们，我们回房去\N{\rEng}Come on, kids. We're going back to the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.28,1:16:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,乔\N{\rEng}Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.02,1:17:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,古巴 古巴\N{\rEng}Cuba, Cuba!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.80,1:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,最尊敬的先生们\N{\rEng}Most respected gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.72,1:18:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,请允许我欢迎你们光临哈瓦那市\N{\rEng}Alow me to welcome you to the City of Havana.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.16,1:18:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要谢谢这个卓越的美国实业家团…\N{\rEng}I want to thank this distinguished group of American industrialists...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.27,1:18:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,…持续跟古巴合作\N{\rEng}for continuing to work with Cuba
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.96,1:18:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在她整个历史当中的…\N{\rEng}for the greatest period of prosperity
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.86,1:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,最繁荣的时期里\N{\rEng}in her entire history.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.13,1:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉姆·萧先生\N{\rEng}Mr. William Shaw
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.43,1:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,代表通用水果公司\N{\rEng}representing the General Fruit Company.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.13,1:18:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,康戈德和丹特二位先生\N{\rEng}Messrs Corngold and Dant
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.97,1:18:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来自联合电话电报公司\N{\rEng}of United Telephone and Telegraph Company.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.07,1:18:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,佩蒂先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Petty
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.95,1:19:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,泛美矿业公司的地区副总裁\N{\rEng}regional Vice President of the Pan American Mining Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.61,1:19:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特·艾伦先生 南美糖业公司\N{\rEng}Mr. Robert Allen of South American Sugar.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.05,1:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,以及迈克尔·柯利昂尼先生 来自内华达州\N{\rEng}Mr. Michael Corleone of Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.06,1:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,代表我们观光休闲活动事业的合作者\N{\rEng}representing our associates in tourism and leisure activities.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.86,1:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我的老朋友及合作伙伴 来自佛罗里达的\N{\rEng}And my old friend and associate from Florida.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.97,1:19:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,海门·罗斯先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Hyman Roth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.25,1:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意借此机会感谢联合电话电报公司…\N{\rEng}I would like to take this opportunity to thank United Telephone and Telegraph
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.12,1:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱的圣诞礼物\N{\rEng}for their lovely Christmas gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.75,1:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一部纯金电话机\N{\rEng}A solid gold telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.35,1:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也许各位先生愿意看一看\N{\rEng}Perhaps you gentlemen would like to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.63,1:19:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 总统先生 - 什么事？\N{\rEng}- Mr. President? - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.70,1:19:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你能谈谈叛乱活动的情况\N{\rEng}Perhaps you would discuss the status of rebel activity
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.92,1:19:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,以及它对我们的生意意味着什么？\N{\rEng}and what this can mean to our businesses?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.43,1:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rEng}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.53,1:19:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,蛮沉的东西\N{\rEng}Heavy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.10,1:19:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要向你们保证\N{\rEng}I want to assure you that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.37,1:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然叛乱分子在拉斯维利亚斯省发起了惊人的军事活动\N{\rEng}although the rebels have mounted an impressive campaign in Las Willas
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.22,1:20:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的参谋们有把握地表明\N{\rEng}my staff indicates, with assurance
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.47,1:20:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能在新年前 把他们赶出圣克拉拉城\N{\rEng}that we'll drive them out of the City of Santa Clara before the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.02,1:20:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我要你们都放心\N{\rEng}And I want to put you all at ease.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.01,1:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们绝不容许游击队 出现在赌场或游泳池\N{\rEng}We will tolerate no guerrillas in the casinos or the swimming pools.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.85,1:20:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他们在抓捕\N{\rEng}He said that they're making an arrest
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.82,1:20:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,几分钟后会让我们通过\N{\rEng}and in a few minutes he'll let us through.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.06,1:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 约翰尼 - 没什么{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}- Johnny. - It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.35,1:20:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是些蟊贼，警察在肃清他们{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Just some lousy bandits.The police are cleaning them up.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.55,1:20:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,……菲德尔{\fs12}[卡斯特罗]{\r}万岁！\N{\rEng}....Viva Fidel!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.81,1:21:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐\N{\rEng}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.72,1:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我的年龄没弄错\N{\rEng}I hope my age is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.80,1:21:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我对我的年龄一向很精确的\N{\rEng}I'm always accurate about my age.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.64,1:21:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,切蛋糕之前 一定让大家都看看蛋糕\N{\rEng}Make sure that everybody sees the cake before we cut it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.35,1:21:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常高兴\N{\rEng}I'm very pleased
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.00,1:21:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你们都能这么远前来，与我相聚\N{\rEng}you're all able to come from such distances to be with me today.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.30,1:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当一个人到了他生命中的这一时间点\N{\rEng}When a man comes to this point in his life
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.53,1:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要把他受上天眷顾的事业交付出去\N{\rEng}he wants to turn over the things he's been blessed with.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.20,1:21:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,把它们交付给朋友们\N{\rEng}Turn them over to friends
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.12,1:21:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一种奖励，给他拥有的朋友们\N{\rEng}as a reward for the friends he's had.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.43,1:21:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也是为确保…\N{\rEng}and to make sure...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.46,1:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在他身后，一切能顺利进行\N{\rEng}that everything goes well after he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.80,1:21:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还有好多年呢\N{\rEng}Not for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.00,1:21:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.84,1:21:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，走着瞧吧，医生们不会同意\N{\rEng}Yeah, we'll see. The doctors would disagree
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.40,1:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们又知道什么？\N{\rEng}but what do they know?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.07,1:22:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都是我们在哈瓦那成就的奇迹\N{\rEng}These are wonderful things that we've achieved in Havana
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.20,1:22:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,由此开始毫无止境\N{\rEng}and there's no limit to where we can go from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.31,1:22:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这种政府知道如何协助商业，如何去鼓励它…\N{\rEng}This kind of government knows how to help business, to encourage it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.24,1:22:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的酒店，更大，更时髦…\N{\rEng}The hotels here are bigger and swankier
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.47,1:22:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,超过我们在维加斯设立的任何粗糙的场所\N{\rEng}than any of the rough joints in we put in Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.40,1:22:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们要感谢在古巴政府的朋友们\N{\rEng}We can thank our friends in the Cuban government
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.45,1:22:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已提供了卡车工会一半现金，以美元兑美元汇率\N{\rEng}which has put up half the cash with the Teamsters on a dollar for dollar basis
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.35,1:22:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,已经放宽了进口的限制\N{\rEng}has relaxed restrictions on imports.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.28,1:22:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要说的是\N{\rEng}What I'm saying is
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.22,1:22:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在有了我们一直所需要的…\N{\rEng}that we have now what we have always needed:
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.65,1:22:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,与政府的真正合伙关系\N{\rEng}Real partnership with a government.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.68,1:22:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小一点\N{\rEng}Smaller piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.38,1:22:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都认识迈克尔·柯利昂尼\N{\rEng}You all know Michael Corleone
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.03,1:22:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们都记得他父亲\N{\rEng}and we all remember his father.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.32,1:22:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在我退休或死亡的时候\N{\rEng}At the time of my retirement, or death
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.10,1:22:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我移交我在哈瓦那的所有经营权益…\N{\rEng}I turn over all my interests in the Havana operation
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.63,1:22:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,给他管理\N{\rEng}to his control.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.16,1:22:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…\N{\rEng}But
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.20,1:23:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们全都有份\N{\rEng}all of you will share.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.26,1:23:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,国有部分给湖村路的人\N{\rEng}The Nacionale will go to the Lakeville Road Boys
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.14,1:23:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,卡普利归柯利昂尼家族\N{\rEng}the Capri to the Corleone family
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.36,1:23:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,塞维拉毕特摩也是\N{\rEng}the Sevilla Biltmore also
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.97,1:23:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，新港的艾迪拉文，将引进潘尼诺兄弟\N{\rEng}but Eddie Levine of new port will bring in the Pennino brothers
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.74,1:23:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,迪诺和艾迪\N{\rEng}Dino and Eddie
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.30,1:23:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,分一份，还有管理实际的赌场经营\N{\rEng}for a piece and also to handle the actual casino operations.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.74,1:23:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还留了一份，给几个内华达的朋友\N{\rEng}And we've saved a piece for some friends in Nevada
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.44,1:23:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,以确定家乡的事都能够顺利\N{\rEng}to make sure that things go smoothly back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.28,1:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你们都好好享用蛋糕\N{\rEng}I want all of you to enjoy your cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.25,1:23:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…吃吧！\N{\rEng}So, enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.32,1:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐\N{\rEng}Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.22,1:23:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天看见一件有趣的事发生\N{\rEng}I saw an interesting thing happen today.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.02,1:23:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一个叛乱者被军警逮捕\N{\rEng}A rebel was being arrested by the military police.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.22,1:23:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而他不愿被活着带走\N{\rEng}And rather than be taken alive
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.32,1:23:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,宁愿引爆外衣中的手榴弹\N{\rEng}he exploded a grenade he had in his jacket.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.97,1:23:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他炸死了自己，还带上一名指挥的队长\N{\rEng}He killed himself and took a captain of the command with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.47,1:23:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧，约翰尼？\N{\rEng}Right,Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.11,1:23:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那些叛乱者，要知道他们是神经病 - 对，对\N{\rEng}- Those rebels, you know they are lunatics. - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.60,1:23:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是这样\N{\rEng}Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.88,1:23:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这令我想到\N{\rEng}But it occurred to me
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.52,1:24:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那些军人是拿薪水打仗的，叛乱者则不是\N{\rEng}the soldiers are paid to fight the rebels aren't.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.11,1:24:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那告诉了你什么？\N{\rEng}What does that tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.47,1:24:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能赢\N{\rEng}They can win.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.17,1:24:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这国家过去50年来都有叛乱\N{\rEng}This country has had rebels for 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.04,1:24:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们骨子里就这样，相信我，我知道\N{\rEng}It's in their blood. Believe me, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.90,1:24:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我由20年代就来这里了\N{\rEng}I've been coming here since the Twenties.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.85,1:24:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们经营哈瓦那糖浆出口时，你还是个婴儿\N{\rEng}We were running molasses out of Havana when you were a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.68,1:24:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那些卡车是你父亲所有的\N{\rEng}The trucks were owned by your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.32,1:24:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\rEng}Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.02,1:24:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿我们单独相处时 再讨论这事\N{\rEng}I'd rather we talked about this when we're alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.79,1:24:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那200万一直没到岛上\N{\rEng}The two million never got to the island.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.60,1:24:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要话传出去 说你撤回了那笔钱…\N{\rEng}I wouldn't want it to get around that you held back the money
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.74,1:24:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你对这场叛乱另有看法\N{\rEng}because you have second thoughts about the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.97,1:25:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下，麦克，坐下\N{\rEng}Sit down, Mike. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.18,1:25:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我但愿能活到看见它，和你一起见证\N{\rEng}If I could only live to see it, to be there with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.38,1:25:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都愿意付出，换来20年\N{\rEng}What I wouldn't give for 20 more years.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.35,1:25:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里，被保护着\N{\rEng}Here we are, protected.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.95,1:25:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,自由创造我们的收益，没有基福弗{\fs12}[参议员]{\r}\N{\rEng}Free to make our profits without Kefauver
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.32,1:25:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有该死的司法部，以及调查局\N{\rEng}the goddamn Justice Department and the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.05,1:25:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在90英里之外\N{\rEng}90 miles away
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.69,1:25:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,跟一个友善的政府合伙\N{\rEng}in partnership with a friendly government.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.93,1:25:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,90英里，这不算什么\N{\rEng}90 miles. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.33,1:25:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是一小步，寻求一个想成为美国总统的人\N{\rEng}Just one small step looking for a man that wants to be President of the United States
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.23,1:25:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还有金钱令其成为可能\N{\rEng}and having the cash to make it possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.67,1:25:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\rEng}Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.87,1:25:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们比美国钢铁公司还大\N{\rEng}we're bigger than U.S. Steel.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.22,1:26:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,麦基，你怎么样？好吗？\N{\rEng}Mikey, how are you? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.49,1:26:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，我是弗雷迪·柯利昂尼\N{\rEng}Hi! Freddie Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.58,1:26:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是我哥哥{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Mio frati
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.59,1:26:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷，这一趟啊\N{\rEng}Jesus Christ, what a trip!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.06,1:26:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一路上我都在想“万一有人知道我这里有什么呢？”\N{\rEng}The whole time I'm thinking, "What if somebody knows what I've got in here".
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.70,1:26:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想像吗？\N{\rEng}Can you imagine that?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.71,1:26:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,200万美元放在我旁边的座位上\N{\rEng}Two million dollars on the seat next to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.65,1:26:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦，对不起 - 不，没关系的\N{\rEng}- Excuse me. - No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.20,1:26:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你要数数吗？\N{\rEng}You want to count it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.70,1:27:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,麦基，这到底是搞的什么鬼？\N{\rEng}Mikey, what the hell is going on anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.07,1:27:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全蒙在鼓里\N{\rEng}I'm totally in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.31,1:27:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,家族要在哈瓦那进行一项投资\N{\rEng}The family is making an investment in Havana.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.48,1:27:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是给总统的小礼物\N{\rEng}This is a little gift for the President.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.88,1:27:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了，哈瓦那好极了\N{\rEng}That's great! Havana's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.05,1:27:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是我钟意的城市\N{\rEng}It's my kind of town.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.38,1:27:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有我认识的人在哈瓦那吗？\N{\rEng}Anybody I know in Havana?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.70,1:27:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，海门·罗斯？约翰尼·欧拉？\N{\rEng}Don't know. Hyman Roth, Johnny Ola?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.16,1:27:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我从未见过他们\N{\rEng}No. I've never met them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.46,1:27:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说，麦基，我…\N{\rEng}Listen, Mikey, I'm ...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.03,1:27:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点…\N{\rEng}I'm kind of...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.36,1:27:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这一路上让我有点紧张\N{\rEng}kind of nervous from the trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.06,1:27:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我能…喝杯酒吗？\N{\rEng}Can I...can I get a drink or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.53,1:27:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也许我们可以一起出去\N{\rEng}I thought maybe we'd go out together.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.02,1:27:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道有个地方能消磨下时间，好不好？\N{\rEng}I know a place where we can spend some time together. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.37,1:27:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我想我应该娶一个你娶的那种女人\N{\rEng}Sometimes I think I should have married a woman like you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.63,1:27:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,像凯伊那样\N{\rEng}Like Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.05,1:28:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有孩子，有个家\N{\rEng}Have kids. Have a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.12,1:28:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在我生命中能有一次\N{\rEng}For once in my life
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.58,1:28:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,能更像…爸爸那样\N{\rEng}be more like Pop..
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.78,1:28:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当个儿子并不容易，弗雷多\N{\rEng}It's not easy to be a son, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.95,1:28:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不容易\N{\rEng}It's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.55,1:28:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道妈曾取笑我，她会说…\N{\rEng}You know mama used to tease me she'd say
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.55,1:28:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“你不是我生的\N{\rEng}"You don't belong to me."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.92,1:28:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“你是吉普赛人留在门口的”\N{\rEng}"You were left on the doorstep by gypsies."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.72,1:28:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候我认为那是真的\N{\rEng}Sometimes I think it's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.56,1:28:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是吉普赛人，弗雷多\N{\rEng}You're no gypsy, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.03,1:28:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,麦基，我…\N{\rEng}Mikey... I...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.22,1:28:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前生你的气\N{\rEng}I was mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.64,1:28:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们以前没像这样闲聊过？\N{\rEng}Why didn't we spend time like this before?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.37,1:28:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝一杯，对吧？\N{\rEng}You want a drink, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.23,1:28:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,侍者\N{\rEng}Waiter!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.47,1:28:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,香蕉达其利怎么讲？\N{\rEng}How do you say Banana Daquiri?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.18,1:28:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,香蕉达其利\N{\rEng}Banana Daquiri.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.60,1:29:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就这样？ - 就这样\N{\rEng}- That's it? - That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.98,1:29:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来一杯香蕉达其利\N{\rEng}Uno Banana Daquiri.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.82,1:29:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 香蕉达其利 - 还有...\N{\rEng}- Banana Daquiri. - And...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.21,1:29:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一杯苏打汽水\N{\rEng}and a club soda.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.28,1:29:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员葛瑞明晚从华盛顿飞来\N{\rEng}Senator Geary flies in from Washington tomorrow night
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.07,1:29:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一些人，一些政府的人\N{\rEng}with some people, some government people.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.49,1:29:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你让他们 在哈瓦那好好玩玩\N{\rEng}I want you to show them a good time in Havana.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.09,1:29:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的专长，对吧？\N{\rEng}That's my speciality, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.62,1:29:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我能在某些事上信任你吗，弗雷多？\N{\rEng}Can I trust you with something?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.92,1:29:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，麦克\N{\rEng}Of course, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.43,1:29:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上稍晚时候\N{\rEng}Later in the evening...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.93,1:29:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都被邀请去总统府招待会，迎接新年\N{\rEng}we're all invited to the Presidential Palace reception, bring in the New Year
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.60,1:29:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,结束之后\N{\rEng}After it's over
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.60,1:29:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会用一辆军方的车载我回家，就我一个\N{\rEng}they'll take me home in a military car, alone
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.46,1:29:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保护我\N{\rEng}For my protection.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.10,1:29:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在我到达酒店前…\N{\rEng}Before I reach my hotel
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.30,1:29:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我会被刺杀\N{\rEng}I'll be assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.85,1:30:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁？\N{\rEng}Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.72,1:30:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯\N{\rEng}Roth.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.59,1:30:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是罗斯想在我家里杀我\N{\rEng}It was Roth who tried to kill me in my home.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.33,1:30:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是罗斯\N{\rEng}It was Roth all along.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.95,1:30:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他装得好像我是他的儿子\N{\rEng}He acts like I'm his son
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.06,1:30:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他的接班人\N{\rEng}his successor.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.85,1:30:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但他以为他会一直活下去\N{\rEng}But he thinks he's gonna live forever
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.56,1:30:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他要我出局\N{\rEng}and he wants me out.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.94,1:30:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么能帮上忙？\N{\rEng}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.51,1:30:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要照旧，像是你什么也不知道\N{\rEng}You just go along, as if you know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.66,1:30:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经有所行动\N{\rEng}I've already made my move.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.55,1:30:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么行动？\N{\rEng}What move?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.54,1:30:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,海门·罗斯永远见不到这个新年\N{\rEng}Hyman Roth won't see the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.42,1:31:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你要放轻松点 他会开处方\N{\rEng}Says you have to take it easy. And he's gonna give you a prescription.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.22,1:31:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他明天会再来 - 我要我自己的医生\N{\rEng}- He'll be back tomorrow. - I want my own doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.59,1:31:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,让他从迈阿密飞过来\N{\rEng}Fly him in from Miami.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.02,1:31:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不信任不会说英文的医生\N{\rEng}I don't trust a doctor who can't speak English.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.82,1:31:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你 先生{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r} - 晚安{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\rEng}- Gracias, senor - Buenas noches
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.65,1:31:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的，到下面赌场吧\N{\rEng}Honey, go down to the casino.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.62,1:31:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你确定你感觉好些了\N{\rEng}If you sure you're feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.41,1:31:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉没事了\N{\rEng}Feel fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.87,1:31:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,去玩宾果游戏吧！\N{\rEng}Play the bingo game.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.86,1:31:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 幸会，保罗先生，请自便 - 谢谢\N{\rEng}- Nice to see you, Mr. Paul. Just make yourself home. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.54,1:31:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的第六感告诉我 你哥哥弗雷多\N{\rEng}My sixth sense tells me your brother Fredo
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.56,1:31:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,带来一个装满钱的箱包\N{\rEng}brought a bag full of money.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.97,1:31:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里？\N{\rEng}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.14,1:31:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你要退出？\N{\rEng}You're pulling out?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.70,1:31:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想要…\N{\rEng}Just want to...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.40,1:31:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想要等等\N{\rEng}Just want to wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.26,1:31:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉如何？\N{\rEng}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.55,1:31:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕\N{\rEng}Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.05,1:32:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意付400万，只要能不疼痛地尿一泡\N{\rEng}I'd give four million just to be able to take a piss without hurting.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.21,1:32:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谁派人杀了弗兰克·潘坦吉利？\N{\rEng}Who had Frank Pentangeli killed?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.66,1:32:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,罗萨托兄弟\N{\rEng}The Rosato brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.20,1:32:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.82,1:32:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是谁给的许可？\N{\rEng}but who gave the go-ahead?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.20,1:32:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我没有\N{\rEng}I know I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.80,1:32:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个孩子，从小和我一起长大\N{\rEng}There was this kid I grew up with.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.65,1:32:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他比我年轻\N{\rEng}He was younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.84,1:32:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,算是仰望我吧，你懂的\N{\rEng}Sort of looked up to me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.38,1:32:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们…\N{\rEng}We...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.13,1:32:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一起做了我们的第一票\N{\rEng}did our first work together.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.64,1:32:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在街头闯出一条路\N{\rEng}Worked our way out of the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.30,1:32:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,事情很顺利，多数时候我们都成功了\N{\rEng}Things were good. We made the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.70,1:32:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,禁酒时期\N{\rEng}During Prohibition
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.20,1:32:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把糖浆运到加拿大 发了笔大财\N{\rEng}we ran molasses into Canada. Made a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.54,1:32:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲也是\N{\rEng}Your father too.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.12,1:32:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如同其他人一样 我爱他\N{\rEng}As much as anyone, I loved him
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.78,1:32:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而且信任他\N{\rEng}and trusted him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.69,1:33:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不久之后，他有了个主意\N{\rEng}Later on he had an idea
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.64,1:33:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去建一座城市\N{\rEng}to build a city
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.82,1:33:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,建在沙漠当中，给要去西岸的军人中途停留之用\N{\rEng}out of a desert stop-over for G.I.s going to the West Coast.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.39,1:33:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子的名字是莫·格林\N{\rEng}That kid's name was Moe Greene
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.32,1:33:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他所创建的城市是拉斯维加斯\N{\rEng}and the city he invented was Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.42,1:33:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个了不起的人\N{\rEng}This was a great man.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.90,1:33:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一个有眼光、有胆量的人\N{\rEng}A man of vision and guts.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.55,1:33:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但却没有一块牌匾，或一个路标…\N{\rEng}And there isn't even a plaque, or a signpost
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.00,1:33:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,或是铜像，在那城里纪念他\N{\rEng}or statue of him in that town.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.84,1:33:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有人…\N{\rEng}Someone...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.80,1:33:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,将一颗子弹射入他的眼睛\N{\rEng}put a bullet through his eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.70,1:33:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人知道是谁下的命令\N{\rEng}No one knows who gave the order.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.88,1:33:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,当我听说时，我没有生气\N{\rEng}When I heard it, I wasn't angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.18,1:33:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道莫，我知道他刚愎自用\N{\rEng}I knew Moe, I knew he was headstrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.38,1:33:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,说话大声，说得难听\N{\rEng}Talking loud, saying stupid things.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.71,1:33:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以当他死时\N{\rEng}So when he turned up dead
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.62,1:33:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我随它去了\N{\rEng}I let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.85,1:33:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我对自己说\N{\rEng}And I said to myself
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.10,1:34:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这，是我们自己选择的生意\N{\rEng}This is the business we've chosen.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.36,1:34:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有问\N{\rEng}I didn't ask
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.09,1:34:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁下的令\N{\rEng}who gave the order
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.22,1:34:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那和生意一点关系也没有\N{\rEng}because it had nothing to do with business.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.70,1:34:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在你房间箱包里的200万\N{\rEng}That two million in a bag in your room
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.63,1:34:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进去 睡一会儿\N{\rEng}I'm going in to take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.80,1:34:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等我醒来\N{\rEng}When I wake
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.00,1:34:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果钱在桌子上\N{\rEng}if the money is on the table
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.56,1:34:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道我有了个合伙人\N{\rEng}I know I have a partner.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.95,1:34:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是，我就知道我没有了\N{\rEng}If it isn't, I know I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.86,1:35:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，在座的是否都认识？\N{\rEng}All right, does everybody know everybody here?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.16,1:35:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是葛瑞参议员，你认识他的\N{\rEng}This is senator Geary, you know him.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.92,1:35:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗，参议员 - 见到你很高兴，麦克\N{\rEng}- How are you, senator? - Good to see you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.92,1:35:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴我们这次能共聚\N{\rEng}I'm glad we spend this time together.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.65,1:35:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，这位是弗罗里达的佩顿参议员\N{\rEng}Mike, this is senator Payton from Florida
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.85,1:35:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗，麦克？\N{\rEng}How ya doin', Mike?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.84,1:35:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约的德马克法官\N{\rEng}Judge DeMalco from New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.61,1:35:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗，先生？\N{\rEng}How do you do, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.42,1:35:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很好，谢谢 - 马里兰的瑞姆参议员\N{\rEng}- How do you do, Sir? - Fine, thank you. -Senator Ream from Maryland
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.72,1:35:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，我一直期待见面\N{\rEng}Mike, I've been looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.11,1:35:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,联合电话电报的弗雷德·康戈德先生\N{\rEng}Fred Corngold from UTT.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.91,1:35:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我认识弗雷德，你好吗？ - 这个弗雷德跳恰恰舞很棒\N{\rEng}- I know Fred, how are you? - That Freddie does a mean Cha Cha Cha
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.31,1:35:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,待会可要留神\N{\rEng}so watch out later around.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.52,1:35:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，是吗？\N{\rEng}Oh he does, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.77,1:36:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，各位，加油时间到了\N{\rEng}Okay,gentlemen,it's refill time here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.32,1:36:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也许该试试本地饮品，知道吗\N{\rEng}You might try some of those local drinks, you know
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.45,1:36:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,“古巴自由”、“椰果飘香”{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\rEng}"Cuba Libra" "Piña Colada"
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.90,1:36:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我看我试一个…红发的紫罗兰{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I think I'll try one of those redheaded Yolandas.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.72,1:36:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,手到擒来\N{\rEng}That you got!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.05,1:36:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我很乐意{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}，你…\N{\rEng}Con gusto, you got it...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.03,1:36:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰尼\N{\rEng}Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.92,1:36:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不认识我哥哥弗雷多，对不对，约翰尼？\N{\rEng}You don't know my brother Fredo, do you, Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.83,1:36:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰尼·欧拉 弗雷多\N{\rEng}Johnny Ola, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.56,1:36:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从没见过\N{\rEng}We never met.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.62,1:36:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是约翰尼·欧拉 幸会\N{\rEng}Johnny Ola. Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.40,1:36:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，敬哈瓦那的一夜\N{\rEng}Gentlemen, to a night in Havana!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.10,1:36:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 新年快乐 - 新年快乐\N{\rEng}- Happy New Year! - Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.91,1:36:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 新年快乐{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r} - 新年快乐\N{\rEng}- Feliz Año Nuevo! - Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.61,1:36:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里 就在那里 别怕\N{\rEng}It's there, it's there. Don't afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.98,1:36:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，弗雷迪，我们干嘛站着？\N{\rEng}Hey, Freddie, why are we standing?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.88,1:36:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都站着\N{\rEng}Everybody stands.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.38,1:36:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但这值得的 看着 你不会相信这个的\N{\rEng}It's worth it. Watch! You're not gonna believe this.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.31,1:36:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不相信了\N{\rEng}I don't believe it already.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.51,1:36:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,赌50元 对吧？\N{\rEng}50 dollars, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.42,1:36:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,赌了，先生\N{\rEng}You've got a bet, mister.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.50,1:37:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他，那就是超人！\N{\rEng}That's him, that's superman.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.21,1:37:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你们说过吧，我跟你们说过吧？\N{\rEng}Did I tell you or did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.20,1:37:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\rEng}I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.50,1:37:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西一定是假的\N{\rEng}It's got to be fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.91,1:37:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不是假的 那是真的 所以才叫他超人\N{\rEng}Ain't no fake. It's real. That's why he's called Superman.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.81,1:37:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，弗雷迪，弗雷迪\N{\rEng}Hey, Freddy
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.86,1:37:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么找到这地方的？\N{\rEng}where did you find this place?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.92,1:37:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰尼·欧拉告诉我这地方，他带我来过这里\N{\rEng}Johnny Ola told me about this place. He brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.32,1:37:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不相信他，但眼见为实，对吧？\N{\rEng}I didn't believe it but seeing is believing!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.37,1:37:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我眼见了，但仍然不相信\N{\rEng}I see it, but still don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.67,1:37:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,50块，帕特\N{\rEng}50 bucks, Pat.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.66,1:38:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯老头从不到这里来\N{\rEng}Old man Roth would never come here
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.24,1:38:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但老约翰尼对这地方了如指掌\N{\rEng}but old Johnny knows these places like the back of his hand.!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.51,1:38:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,注意看，他用它打断一个夹子了\N{\rEng}Now watch him, he's gonna break a cracker with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.62,1:38:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,打断夹子？我要看他打断一块砖\N{\rEng}Break a cracker? I want to see him break a brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.80,1:38:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以干翻一座大楼\N{\rEng}He could knock down a building.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.44,1:39:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,放轻松，罗斯先生\N{\rEng}Relax, Señor Roth.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.78,1:39:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们送你去医院\N{\rEng}we're taking you to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.87,1:40:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,依我的判断，你会继续得到那些\N{\rEng}And in my judgment, you'll continue to get those,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.31,1:40:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不相信…\N{\rEng}because I don't believe
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.72,1:40:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,艾森豪威尔总统会撤出古巴\N{\rEng}that President Eisenhower well ever pull out of Cuba
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.75,1:40:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们在这个国家还有超过十亿美金的投资\N{\rEng}not as long as we have over one billion dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.08,1:40:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他就不会撤走\N{\rEng}invested in this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.85,1:40:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,美国公众相信不干涉政策…\N{\rEng}The American public believe in non-intervention...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.25,1:40:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多\N{\rEng}Fredo!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.92,1:40:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里？\N{\rEng}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.36,1:40:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去倒杯真正的酒\N{\rEng}I'm gonna get me a real drink
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.76,1:40:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我喝不下…\N{\rEng}because I can't...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.72,1:41:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事耽搁了罗斯先生？\N{\rEng}What kept Mr. Roth?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.09,1:41:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他要来的\N{\rEng}I understood he was coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.22,1:41:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，里弗斯，礼仪怎么说？\N{\rEng}Hey, Reeves, what's the protocol?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.35,1:41:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该在这里待多久？\N{\rEng}How long should we stay?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.94,1:41:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't konw.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.16,1:41:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我想半个小时就可以了\N{\rEng}I think a half hour ought to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.99,1:41:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只要待到新年来临即可\N{\rEng}Just long enough to bring in the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.94,1:42:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是除夕夜 来吧 就一分钟{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\rEng}It's New Year's Eve. Come on, just for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.65,1:43:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有架飞机在等我们\N{\rEng}There's a plane waiting for us
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.26,1:43:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时内带我们到迈阿密，知道吗？\N{\rEng}to take us to Miami in an hour. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.20,1:43:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要闹出太大动静\N{\rEng}Don't make a big thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.08,1:43:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是你，弗雷多\N{\rEng}I know it was you, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.82,1:43:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你伤了我的心！\N{\rEng}You broke my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.52,1:43:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你伤了我的心！\N{\rEng}You broke my heart!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.32,1:44:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于我们的部队在关塔那摩 及圣地牙哥严重的挫败{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Due to serious setbacks to our troops in Guantanamo and Santiago
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.92,1:44:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我在古巴的地位不能维持{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\rEng}my position in Cuba is untenable.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.33,1:44:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我将辞去总统职位以避免更多流血{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I am resigning from office to avoid further bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.86,1:44:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我会立刻离开这座城市{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\rEng}And I shall leave the city immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.67,1:45:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我祝你们好运！{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I wish all of you good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.82,1:45:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多\N{\rEng}Fredo!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.04,1:45:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，跟我一起走\N{\rEng}Come on. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.48,1:45:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是今晚离开这里的唯一方法！\N{\rEng}It's the only way out of here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.69,1:45:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯已经死了！弗雷多\N{\rEng}Roth is dead!Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.65,1:45:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多，跟我来！\N{\rEng}Fredo, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.13,1:45:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然是我哥哥！弗雷多…\N{\rEng}You're still my brother. Fredo...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.85,1:45:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多！\N{\rEng}Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.74,1:46:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,美国公民才行！\N{\rEng}U.S cityzen only
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.04,1:46:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们过去！我是帕特·葛瑞，美国参议员\N{\rEng}Pass through, I'm Pat GEARY of the United States Senate!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.35,1:46:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 请退后 - 拜托，我必须走\N{\rEng}- Get back! - Please, I must leave!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.02,1:47:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔\N{\rEng}Al.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.00,1:47:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,给我拿条湿毛巾\N{\rEng}Get me a wet towel.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.03,1:47:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊知道我回来吗？\N{\rEng}Kay know I'm back?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.83,1:47:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子怎么样？\N{\rEng}What about my boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.46,1:47:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞节你给他送东西了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you get him something for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.42,1:47:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我料理了\N{\rEng}I took care of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.02,1:47:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么？好让我知道\N{\rEng}What was it, so I'll know.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.85,1:47:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是辆小车，有电动马达，他能驾驶\N{\rEng}It was a little car with an electric motor that he can ride in.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.46,1:47:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\rEng}It's nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.45,1:48:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 艾尔\N{\rEng}Thank you, Al.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.31,1:48:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，你们是否能出去一会儿？\N{\rEng}Fellows, could you step outside for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.90,1:48:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥呢？\N{\rEng}Where's my brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.90,1:48:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯坐一艘私人船出来，在迈阿密一家医院\N{\rEng}Roth got out on a private boat. He's in a hospital in Miami.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.19,1:48:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他中风了，但恢复不错\N{\rEng}He had a stroke, but recovered okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.33,1:48:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你的保镖死了\N{\rEng}Your bodyguard is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.95,1:48:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我问弗雷多的事\N{\rEng}I asked about Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.85,1:48:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他逃出来了，一定是在纽约某处\N{\rEng}I think he got out. He must be somewhere in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.98,1:48:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧！\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.60,1:48:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你跟他联系\N{\rEng}I want you to get in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.57,1:48:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他害怕\N{\rEng}I know he's scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.55,1:48:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他一切都没事了\N{\rEng}Tell him everything is all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.60,1:48:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他，我知道罗斯误导了他\N{\rEng}Tell him I know Roth misled him.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.90,1:48:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他并不知道他们想杀我\N{\rEng}That he didn't know they would try to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.07,1:48:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以进来了\N{\rEng}They can come in now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.51,1:49:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还有别的事\N{\rEng}Well, there was something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.30,1:49:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.70,1:49:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？快说，什么事？\N{\rEng}What? Come on, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.41,1:49:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊小产了，孩子没保住！\N{\rEng}Kay had a miscarriage. She lost the baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.64,1:49:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是个男孩吗？\N{\rEng}Was it a boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.91,1:49:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，才三个半月大\N{\rEng}Mike. At three and a half months.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.26,1:49:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能给我个直截了当的答案吗？\N{\rEng}Now, can't you give me a straight answer anymore?!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.30,1:49:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是个男孩吗？\N{\rEng}Was it a boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.33,1:49:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的不知道\N{\rEng}I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.41,1:50:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的小弗雷多 他得了肺炎{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Poor little Fredo, he's got pneumonia.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.87,1:50:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻人 我听说你和你的朋友们在偷东西{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Young man, I hear you and your friends are stealing goods.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.50,1:50:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们连套衣服 也没送到我家去{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}But you don't even send a dress to my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.10,1:50:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不尊重我{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}No respect!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.84,1:50:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我有三个女儿{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You know I've got three daughters.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.51,1:51:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的地盘{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}This is my neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.18,1:51:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你与你的朋友们 应该对我尊敬些{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You and your friends should show me some respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.25,1:51:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该让我沾一嘴{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You should let me wet my beak a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.22,1:51:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你与你的朋友们{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I hear you and your friends
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.52,1:51:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,每人分得600元{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}cleared $600 each.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.66,1:51:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,每人给我200元保护费{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Give me $200 each, for your own protection.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.49,1:51:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就忘了这次侮辱{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}And I'll forget the insult.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.12,1:51:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们年轻的混蛋该学着…{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You young punks have to learn
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.97,1:51:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,尊重像我这样的人{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}to respect a man like me!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.86,1:51:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,否则条子会到你们家去{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Otherwise the cops will come to your house.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.07,1:51:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们的家就被毁了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}And your family will be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.62,1:51:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，如果我弄错了你们偷的数目{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Of course if I'm wrong about how much you stole
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.57,1:51:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以少收一点 每人少收100元{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I'll take a little less.And by less,I only mean a hundred bucks less.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.75,1:51:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拒绝我，了解吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Now don't refuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.14,1:51:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 了解吗，老乡{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r} - 我了解{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}- Understand, paesano? - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.75,1:52:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我与我的朋友们把钱都分了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}My friends and I share all the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.75,1:52:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我得先和他们谈{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}So first, I have to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.89,1:52:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去和你的朋友谈谈{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Tell your friends
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.36,1:52:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要很多，沾一嘴而已\N{\rEng}I don't want a lot. Just enough to wet my beak.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.22,1:52:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别怕告诉他们{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Don't be afraid to tell them!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.06,1:52:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,600块{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}600 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.58,1:52:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不付呢？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Suppose we don't pay?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.75,1:52:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们那帮人，泰西欧{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You know his gang, Tessio.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.10,1:52:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的野兽！{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Real animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.75,1:52:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,马兰扎诺让法努奇在这一带混{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Maranzalla himself let Fanucci work this neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.77,1:52:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他与条子有来往！{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}He's got connections with the cops, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.64,1:52:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须付给他{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}We have to pay him.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.20,1:52:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,每人200块，大家同意吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}$200 each...everybody agreed?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.34,1:52:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们干嘛得付给他？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Why do we have to pay him?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.82,1:52:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,维多 这件事交给我们{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Vito, leave this to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.64,1:52:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他只有一个人 我们有三个{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}He's one person, we're three.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.28,1:52:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他有枪 我们也有枪{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}He's got guns, we've got guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.58,1:52:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛要将我们的血汗钱送给他{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Why should we give him the money we sweated for?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.06,1:53:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是他的地盘{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}This is his neighborhood!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.05,1:53:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道有两个赌马经纪 什么也不给法努奇{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I know two bookies who don't give anything to Fanucci.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.53,1:53:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不付钱给法努奇{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}They don't pay Fanucci.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.04,1:53:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们不付钱给法努奇{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}If they don't pay Fanucci
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.75,1:53:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就是另外有人为马兰扎诺去收{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}then somebody else collects for Maranzalla!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.63,1:53:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们付钱给他，我们都会好过些{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}We'll all be better off if we pay him.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.93,1:53:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.50,1:53:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在说的仅止于这个房间{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Now what I say stays in this room.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.35,1:53:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你俩愿意{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}If you both like
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.20,1:53:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要不就每人给我50元付给法努奇？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}why not give me $50 each to pay Fanucci?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.13,1:53:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证他会接受我给他的钱{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I guarantee he'll accept what I give him.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.72,1:54:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果法努奇说200元{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}If Fanucci says $200
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.74,1:54:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是要那么多，维多{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}he means it, Vito!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.60,1:54:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我会和他讲道理{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I'll reason with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.08,1:54:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,都交给我吧！{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.20,1:54:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我会料理一切的\N{\rEng}I'll take care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.24,1:54:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不对我的朋友说谎{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I never lie to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.37,1:54:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,明天你们俩都去和法努奇谈{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Tomorrow you both go talk to Fanucci.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.10,1:54:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他会要那笔钱{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}He'll ask for the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.56,1:54:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他 他要什么你们都给{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Tell him you'll pay whatever he wants.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.97,1:54:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,别和他争论{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Don't argue with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.77,1:54:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我会去让他同意{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Then I'll go and get him to agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.57,1:54:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,既然他那么强硬 别和他争论{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Don't argue with him, since he's so tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.05,1:54:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么可能让他少要？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}How can you get him to take less?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.75,1:54:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的事{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}That's my business.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.41,1:54:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只要记得我帮了你们一个忙{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Just remember that I did you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.07,1:54:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一言为定？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}  - 好{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}- Is it a deal? - Si.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.99,1:55:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯！{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Salute.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.64,1:55:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯！{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Salute.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.19,1:55:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯！{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Salute.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.31,1:55:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他的家人出去了\N{\rEng}His family's out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.20,1:55:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,法努奇一个人在咖啡馆\N{\rEng}Fanucci's alone in the cafe.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.45,1:55:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,维多 这是我的50元\N{\rEng}Vito, here's my 50 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.85,1:56:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,维多 你确定他会收吗？\N{\rEng}Buona fortuna, are you sure he's going to go for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.04,1:56:15.99,Chs,,0,0,0,,（意大利语）
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.58,1:56:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我会开个他不能拒绝的条件\N{\rEng}I'll make an offer he don't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.40,1:56:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\rEng}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.31,1:56:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来我帽子下有100元{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}It looks like there's - $100 under my hat.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.13,1:57:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我说对了{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.13,1:57:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只有100元{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Only $100...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.60,1:57:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我目前缺钱用{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I'm short of money right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.44,1:57:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我失业了 给我一点时间{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I've been out of work,so just give me a little time.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.34,1:57:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你了解的，对吧？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.00,1:57:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你有胆量，年轻人{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}You've got balls, young man!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.60,1:57:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前怎么没听过你的名字？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}How come I never heard of you before?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.04,1:57:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你非常有胆量{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}You've got a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.53,1:58:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你找份赚大钱的工作{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I'll find you some work for good money.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.50,1:58:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别往心里去，好吧？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}No hard feelings, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.73,1:58:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有我能帮忙的，就告诉我{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}If I can help you, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.90,1:58:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,节日快乐\N{\rEng}Enjoy the festa!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.51,1:58:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·法努奇\N{\rEng}Don FANUCCI.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.06,2:00:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,强迫{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Forzzelando!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.65,2:00:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我来说太暴力了{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Oh, this is too violent for me!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.71,2:03:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那边干什么？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}What've you got there?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.75,2:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\rEng}Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.40,2:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸非常的爱你{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Michael, your father loves you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.52,2:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,奇齐先生，从1942年到现在\N{\rEng}Mr. Cicci, from the year 1942 to the present time,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.25,2:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你受雇于坚科橄榄油公司？\N{\rEng}you were an employee of the Genco Olive Oil Company?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.92,2:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:22.45,2:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但事实上 你是柯利昂尼犯罪组织的成员\N{\rEng}But in actuality you were a member of the Corleone crime organisation.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:29.52,2:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我们叫它柯利昂尼家族，参议员\N{\rEng}No, we called it the Corleone family, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.31,2:09:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们称之为家族\N{\rEng}we called it the family.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.86,2:09:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你的职务是什么？\N{\rEng}What was your position?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.14,2:09:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最开始，跟其他人一样，我是个“士兵”\N{\rEng}At first, like everybody else, I was a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.43,2:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\rEng}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.57,2:09:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一个扣子，你知道的，参议员，得了\N{\rEng}A button, you know, Senator. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.57,2:09:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不知道 告诉我\N{\rEng}No, I don't know. Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:47.63,2:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,当老板说给某人“钉个扣子”的时候\N{\rEng}When the boss says "push a button" on a guy,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.37,2:09:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我就钉个扣子\N{\rEng}I push a button.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.82,2:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗，参议员？\N{\rEng}See, Senator?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:53.23,2:09:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,奎斯特先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Questadt.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.07,2:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是说你杀人？ - 我什么？\N{\rEng}- You mean you kill people? - I what?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:57.53,2:09:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀人，按照…\N{\rEng}You kill people at the...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.40,2:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,按照你上级的命令\N{\rEng}at the behest of your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:06.19,2:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对，没错，大律师\N{\rEng}Yeah, that's right, counsel.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.81,2:10:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而你们…家族的…老大，是迈克尔·柯利昂尼\N{\rEng}And the head of your family is Michael Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.24,2:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对，律师，迈克尔·柯利昂尼，对了\N{\rEng}Yeah, Counsellor. Michael Corleone, right.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:16.44,2:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾得到过直接来自迈克尔·柯利昂尼的这种命令吗？\N{\rEng}Did you ever get such an order directly from Michael Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:21.05,2:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，我从没和他说过话\N{\rEng}No, I never talked to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.20,2:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,奇齐先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Cicci
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.75,2:10:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你能否详述一点你的答案？\N{\rEng}Could you amplify your answer a bit, please?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:27.42,2:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要做什么？\N{\rEng}Do what?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:29.16,2:10:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你能否多说点答案？我…\N{\rEng}Could you expand on your answer? I'm...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.22,2:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,特别有兴趣知道…\N{\rEng}particularly interested in knowing...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.52,2:10:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是否总是有中间缓冲？\N{\rEng}was there always a buffer involved?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:36.92,2:10:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,某个人在你和你可能下命令的上级之间\N{\rEng}Someone in between you and your possible superiors who gave the order.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.45,2:10:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对，是的，缓冲\N{\rEng}Right, yeah, a buffer.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.35,2:10:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,家族中有许多缓冲\N{\rEng}The family had a lot of buffers!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.96,2:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,奇齐先生，你也许觉得这很好玩\N{\rEng}Mr. Cicci, you may find this very amusing,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.02,2:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但我跟你保证，本委员会的成员不这么想\N{\rEng}but I promise you that the members of this committee do not.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.86,2:11:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我一件事，妈{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Tell me something, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:26.60,2:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在父亲内心深处，他想些什么？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}What did Papa think deep in his heart?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:36.43,2:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直很坚强{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}He was being strong.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.60,2:11:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为他的家庭而坚强{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Strong for his family.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:50.58,2:11:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但除了为他的家庭坚强以外{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}But by being strong for his family
Dialogue: 0,2:12:00.62,2:12:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他会不会失去它？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}could he lose it?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.48,2:12:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想你妻子及失去的孩子{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}You're thinking about your wife about the baby you lost.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.95,2:12:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但你跟你妻子总是还能生孩子{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}But you and your wife can always have another baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:18.70,2:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我是说…失去他的家庭{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}No, I meant... lose his family,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.06,2:12:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但你永远不会失去你的家庭{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}But you can never lose your family.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:30.46,2:12:31.52,Chs,,0,0,0,,不会{\fs12}[意大利语]
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.93,2:12:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,时代变了{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Times are changing.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:03.01,2:13:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不，是我的荣幸，不要钱{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}It's my pleasure. I don't want money.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:06.55,2:13:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把它当礼物吧{\fs12}[意大利语] - 谢谢{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}- Take it as a gift. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:10.14,2:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么我可以帮忙的 你来 我们谈谈{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}If there's something I can do for you, you come, we talk.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.81,2:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.59,2:13:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,柯伦波太太，你为什么来找我？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Signora Colombo, why did you come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:37.76,2:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子告诉我，问问你能否帮我{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Your wife told me to ask if you could help me.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.73,2:13:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她有大麻烦{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}She's in bad trouble.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.67,2:13:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他的邻居跟房东抱怨她的狗{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Her neighbors complained to the landlord about her dog.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.06,2:13:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫她把那动物丢掉{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}He told her to get rid of the animal.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:55.03,2:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但她的小儿子爱那条狗{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}But her little boy loves that dog.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.57,2:14:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她把它藏了起来{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}So she hid it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:01.14,2:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但当房东发现之后{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}When the landlord found out
Dialogue: 0,2:14:03.70,2:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他很生气 叫她搬走{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}he got mad and told her to leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:05.64,2:14:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在即便她把狗弄走 也无法住下去了{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Now she can't stay even if she gets rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:11.00,2:14:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我好惭愧{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I'm so ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:13.15,2:14:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他说要叫警察来 把我们扔到街上{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}He said he'd get the police to throw us out on the street.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:20.35,2:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很同情，不过…{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:24.21,2:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我能给你一些钱帮你搬家{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I could give you a couple dollars to help you move.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:28.35,2:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能搬{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:30.92,2:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你和他谈谈{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I want you to talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.65,2:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他我想要住在这里{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Tell him I want to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.15,2:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的房东叫什么名字？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}What's your landlord's name?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.06,2:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他是罗伯特先生{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}His name is Signor Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:48.63,2:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他住在第四街 离这很近\N{\rEng}He lives on Fourth Street, near here.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.79,2:14:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们打破窗户 弄脏地板{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}They break the windows, they dirty the floors...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:55.53,2:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是猪，对吧？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}A real pig-sty, eh?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.34,2:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特先生{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Mr.Roberto
Dialogue: 0,2:15:15.11,2:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是维多·柯利昂尼{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}My name is Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:18.07,2:15:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,柯伦波太太是我妻子的朋友{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Signora Colombo is a friend of my wife.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.48,2:15:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她说她被驱逐了，没有正当理由{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}She says she's been evicted for no good reason.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:25.33,2:15:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个穷寡妇，没人照料她{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}She's a poor widow, she has nobody to take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:29.41,2:15:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有亲人 没有钱{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}She has no relatives, no money.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:32.65,2:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她所有的只是这一带的邻居{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}All she has is this neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:34.21,2:15:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经把那地方租给另外一家了{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I already rented the place to another family.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:42.11,2:15:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过她我会跟你谈谈{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I told her that I'd talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.48,2:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,说你是个讲道理的人{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}That you're a reasonable man.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:49.39,2:15:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她弄走了那惹麻烦的动物{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}She got rid of the animal that caused all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:53.39,2:15:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让她留下来吧！{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}So let her stay.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.29,2:16:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是不是西西里人？{\fs12}[意大利语] - 不 我是卡拉布列兹人{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}- Are you Sicilian? - No, I'm Calabrese.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.23,2:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们实际上是同乡，帮我一个忙{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}We're practically paesani, do me this favor.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:05.93,2:16:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我都租出去了，会被人当傻子看的{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I already rented it! I'll look like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:10.90,2:16:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而且新房客的房租要高一些{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Besides, the new tenants pay more rent.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:12.80,2:16:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一个月多少钱？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}How much more a month?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:15.60,2:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,5块钱{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Five bucks.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.24,2:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是先付6个月的涨价租金{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Here's six months increase in advance.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:25.06,2:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但别告诉她，她的自尊心很强{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}But don't tell her about it. She's very proud.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:29.20,2:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,6个月到了再来找我{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Come see me in another six months.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:33.67,2:16:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，那条狗留下，对吧？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Of course, the dog stays. Right?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:37.51,2:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那条狗留下{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}The dog stays.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:39.04,2:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你算什么？来对我下命令？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Who the hell are you to come give me orders?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:46.82,2:16:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小心我把你那 西西里屁股踢到街上{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Watch out or I'll kick your Sicilian ass right into the street!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:53.32,2:16:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我一个忙 我不会忘记的{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Do me this favor. I won't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:59.08,2:17:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你在这一带的朋友打听打听我{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Ask your friends in the neighborhood about me.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:03.63,2:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会告诉你，我是懂得报答的人{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}They'll tell you I know how to return a favor.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:12.80,2:17:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好一个人物哦{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}What a character!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:21.66,2:17:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,维多 那个叫罗伯特的房东来了{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}That landlord is here... Roberto
Dialogue: 0,2:17:25.04,2:17:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个租屋屋主{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}the one who owns those ratholes.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:35.80,2:17:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直在这一带打听你{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}He's been asking all around the neighborhood about you.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:41.77,2:17:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:45.84,2:17:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我没打扰你，唐·维多{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I hope I'm not disturbing you, Don Vito.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:50.48,2:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有何效劳之处，唐·罗伯特{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}What can I do for you, Don Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:53.71,2:17:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真是场误会，圣母玛丽亚{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}What a misunderstanding! Holy Mary!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:58.20,2:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,柯伦波太太当然能留下来{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Of course Signora Colombo can stay!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.05,2:18:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Grazie...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:05.90,2:18:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·维多{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Don Vito
Dialogue: 0,2:18:07.40,2:18:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我来归还你给我的钱\N{\rEng}I'm giving back the money you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:12.02,2:18:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二 三 四 五 六 全都在这\N{\rEng}Un, due, three, four, five, six, tutt'!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:18.49,2:18:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟，唐·维多，钱并非一切{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Because after all, Don Vito, money isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:31.90,2:18:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我能坐下吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Can I sit down?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:34.83,2:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.49,2:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你对那寡妇的仁慈令我自己惭愧{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Your kindness to that widow made me ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.45,2:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,房租和以前一样\N{\rEng}The rent stays like before!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:51.74,2:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而且…我会降价{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I'll even lower it.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:57.70,2:19:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我减5元{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I'll lower it $5.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:03.11,2:19:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我减10元{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I'll lower it $10!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.41,2:19:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…\N{\rEng}Grazie...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.42,2:19:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我能请你喝咖啡吗？{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Can I offer you some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:13.71,2:19:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我约会快迟到了{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I'm late for an appointment!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.25,2:19:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次不行 也许改天吧！{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I can't this time! Ask me another time!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:23.49,2:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅我现在失陪了{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}You'll have to excuse me for now.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:30.79,2:19:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我能留久一点{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}I wish I could stay longer!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:39.19,2:19:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只要叫我 我就会来的{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Just call me and I'll be here!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:45.67,2:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:54.46,2:19:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会回来了，他会躲到布朗克斯去{\fs12}[意大利语]\N{\rEng}He won't be back. He'll hide out in the Bronx!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:13.31,2:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,维多，你认为如何？天佑美国\N{\rEng}Vito, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:15.91,2:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会做上大生意的\N{\rEng}We'll make a big business!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:25.42,2:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 纽约市 - 不介意大声点吧？\N{\rEng}- New York City. - Would you mind speaking loud, please?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.86,2:20:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约市\N{\rEng}New York City.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.62,2:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是不是维多·柯利昂尼之子？ - 是的，我是\N{\rEng}- Are you the son of Vito Corleone? - Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.42,2:20:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪里出生？\N{\rEng}Where was he born?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:36.31,2:20:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,西西里的柯利昂尼村\N{\rEng}Corleone, Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:38.20,2:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他是不是有时使用一个别称\N{\rEng}Did he at times use an alias
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.26,2:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在特定圈子里被称为“教父”\N{\rEng}that was known in certain circles as Godfather?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:44.96,2:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,教父是一个代称，是他的朋友用的\N{\rEng}Godfather is a term that was used by his friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:48.20,2:20:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一是爱戴，一是尊敬\N{\rEng}One of affection and one of respect.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.78,2:20:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,主席先生！\N{\rEng}Mr. Chairman
Dialogue: 0,2:20:53.15,2:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意证实证人的陈述\N{\rEng}I would like to verify the witness' statement.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:56.70,2:21:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,多年来随着我的选民中意大利移民数目的增长\N{\rEng}For years now a growing number of my constituents have been of Italian descent.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.95,2:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我逐步了解他们很多\N{\rEng}and I've come to know them well.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.75,2:21:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的支持和他们的友谊，令我光荣\N{\rEng}They have honoured me with their support and with their friendship.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.00,2:21:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以骄傲地说\N{\rEng}Me, I can proudly say
Dialogue: 0,2:21:10.20,2:21:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一些极为要好的朋友就是美籍意大利人\N{\rEng}that some of my very best friends are Italian-Americans.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.50,2:21:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然而，主席先生，在这个时刻，不幸我必须离席\N{\rEng}However, Mr. Chairman, at this time, unfortunately I have to leave these proceedings
Dialogue: 0,2:21:20.60,2:21:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,去主持我自己委员会的一个极重要的会议\N{\rEng}in order to preside over a very important meeting of my own committee.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:25.66,2:21:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但在我离开之前，我一定要说\N{\rEng}Before I leave, I do want to say this
Dialogue: 0,2:21:28.75,2:21:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这些黑手党的听证会 不管怎么样\N{\rEng}that these hearings on the Mafia are in no way whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,2:21:33.18,2:21:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是对意大利人的一种诽谤\N{\rEng}a slur upon the great Italian people.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.90,2:21:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我可以声明，根据我自己的知识和经验\N{\rEng}I can state from my own knowledge and experience
Dialogue: 0,2:21:39.31,2:21:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,美籍意大利人是这个国家里最为忠诚，最守法…\N{\rEng}that Italian-Americans are among the most loyal, most law-abiding,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:44.45,2:21:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,爱国、勤恳的美国公民中的一员\N{\rEng}patriotic, hard-working American citizens in this land.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:49.00,2:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这将会是一个耻辱，主席先生\N{\rEng}It would be a shame, Mr. Chairman
Dialogue: 0,2:21:51.57,2:21:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,假如我们允许几颗老鼠屎 玷污了一锅汤的话\N{\rEng}if we allowed a few rotten apples to give a bad name to the whole barrel.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:56.62,2:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为从伟大的克里斯多弗·哥伦布{\fs12}[意大利人]{\r}时代…\N{\rEng}Because from the time of the great Christopher Columbus
Dialogue: 0,2:21:59.40,2:22:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,经过恩里克·费米{\fs12}[意大利裔科学家]{\r}时代\N{\rEng}up through the time of Enrico Fermi
Dialogue: 0,2:22:02.12,2:22:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,直到当代\N{\rEng}right upon to the present day.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:04.44,2:22:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,美籍意大利人一直是建设和保卫我们伟大祖国的先锋\N{\rEng}Italian-Americans have been pioneers in building and defending our great nation.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:09.21,2:22:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是土地之盐\N{\rEng}They are the salt of the earth
Dialogue: 0,2:22:11.10,2:22:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也是这国家的脊梁之一\N{\rEng}and they're one of the backbones of this country.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:17.10,2:22:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快，快…\N{\rEng}Come on, come on...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:20.30,2:22:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我确定我们都同意我们可敬的同事\N{\rEng}I'm sure we all agree with our esteemed college.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.25,2:22:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生\N{\rEng}Now, Mr. Corleone
Dialogue: 0,2:22:25.57,2:22:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经被知会了你的合法权利\N{\rEng}you have been advised as to your legal rights.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:28.90,2:22:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一位证人的证词，一位早前的证人\N{\rEng}We have testimony from a witness, a previous witness
Dialogue: 0,2:22:32.06,2:22:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一位威利·奇齐\N{\rEng}one Willi Cicci.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:35.42,2:22:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他作证说 你是本国最强有力黑手党家族的老大\N{\rEng}He stated that you are head of the most powerful Mafia family in the country.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:39.86,2:22:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是吗？\N{\rEng}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:41.10,2:22:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我不是\N{\rEng}No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:42.30,2:22:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,证人作证说你个人对于…\N{\rEng}The witness testified that you are personally responsible
Dialogue: 0,2:22:45.44,2:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,1947年一位纽约警监的谋杀负有责任\N{\rEng}for the murder of a New York police captain in 1947
Dialogue: 0,2:22:49.51,2:22:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,以及一个和他一起的男人，名叫维吉尔·索洛佐\N{\rEng}and with him a man named Virgil Sollozzo.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:53.42,2:22:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你否认这个吗？ - 是的，我否认\N{\rEng}- Do you deny this? - Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.05,2:23:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,此事是否属实？在…1950年你策划谋杀了…\N{\rEng}Is it true that in the year 1950 you devised the murder
Dialogue: 0,2:23:00.78,2:23:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约所谓“五大家族”的老大\N{\rEng}of the heads of the so called "Five Families" in New York
Dialogue: 0,2:23:04.65,2:23:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,以篡夺并巩固你的不法权力\N{\rEng}to assume and consolidate your nefarious power?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:08.40,2:23:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是彻底的谎言\N{\rEng}It's a complete falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:10.13,2:23:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奎斯特先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Questadt.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:11.73,2:23:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是否属实，你控股拉斯维加斯三家主要酒店？\N{\rEng}Is it true you have a controlling interest in three of the major hotels in Las Vegas?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:17.42,2:23:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不是真的\N{\rEng}No, it's not true.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:18.46,2:23:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我拥有那里几家酒店的一些股票\N{\rEng}I own some stock in some of the hotels there
Dialogue: 0,2:23:21.16,2:23:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但数量很少\N{\rEng}but very little.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:25.27,2:23:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有IBM 及电话电报公司的股票\N{\rEng}I also have stock in IBM and IT&T.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:29.80,2:23:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Corleone
Dialogue: 0,2:23:30.70,2:23:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否获利并掌控赌博或毒品业\N{\rEng}do you have any interests or control over gambling or narcotics
Dialogue: 0,2:23:35.20,2:23:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在纽约州 - 不，我没有\N{\rEng}- in the state of New York.? - No, I do not.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:38.70,2:23:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员，我的委托人想要在本委员会面前读一份声明…\N{\rEng}Senator, my client would like to read a statement before this committee.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:41.94,2:23:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,主席先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Chairman
Dialogue: 0,2:23:43.60,2:23:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,主席先生，我认为这篇声明…\N{\rEng}Mr. Chairman,I think this statement...
Dialogue: 0,2:23:46.01,2:23:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,此时是完全不合秩序的\N{\rEng}is totally out of order at this time.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:48.08,2:23:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，我的委托人已以最大诚意回答了…\N{\rEng}Sir, my client has answered every question
Dialogue: 0,2:23:51.25,2:23:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,本委员会提出的每一个问题\N{\rEng}asked by this committee with the up most sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:54.27,2:23:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他并未引用第五修正案\N{\rEng}He has not taken the Fifth Amendment
Dialogue: 0,2:23:56.07,2:23:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这是他的权利\N{\rEng}as it was his right to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.13,2:24:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以公平起见，这篇声明应该被听到\N{\rEng}so it'll fair is that this statement should be heard!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:01.95,2:24:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我要允许柯利昂尼先生读出他的声明\N{\rEng}No, I'm going to allow Mr. Corleone to read his statement.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:05.42,2:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把它列入记录\N{\rEng}I'll put it in the record.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:08.72,2:24:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,出于澄清我家庭名声的希望\N{\rEng}In the hopes of clearing my family name
Dialogue: 0,2:24:11.96,2:24:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,以及给我的孩子们 公平分享美国生活方式的真心实意\N{\rEng}and the sincere desire to give my children their fair share of the American way of life
Dialogue: 0,2:24:16.07,2:24:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为不玷污他们的姓氏和背景\N{\rEng}without a blemish on their name and background
Dialogue: 0,2:24:19.10,2:24:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我出席这委员会，并给予我的全心合作\N{\rEng}I have appeared before this committee and given it all the cooperation in my part.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.55,2:24:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对于不得不否认自己是一名罪犯\N{\rEng}I consider it a great dishonor to me personal
Dialogue: 0,2:24:28.70,2:24:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我视之为我个人极大的羞辱\N{\rEng}to have to deny that I am a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:32.38,2:24:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望以下几点列入记录\N{\rEng}I wish to have the following noted for the record:
Dialogue: 0,2:24:35.75,2:24:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我在二战中 曾忠诚并体面地为国服役\N{\rEng}That I served my country faithfully and honorably in World War Two
Dialogue: 0,2:24:40.06,2:24:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,并曾因保卫自己国家的行动 而获颁海军十字勋章\N{\rEng}and was awarded the Navy Cross for actions in defence of my country.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:45.75,2:24:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未因任何各种罪名 被捕或被控告\N{\rEng}That I have never been arrested or indicted for any crime what soever.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:50.40,2:24:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没有证据把我跟任何犯罪阴谋联系起来\N{\rEng}That no proof linking me to any criminal conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,2:24:54.44,2:24:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不管它被称作“黑手党”还是“我们的事业”\N{\rEng}whether it is called Mafia or Cosa Nostra
Dialogue: 0,2:24:57.28,2:25:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,或别的什么曾经公开过的，你们希望加诸的名义\N{\rEng}or any other name you wish to give has ever been made public.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:01.87,2:25:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有躲在第五修正案的庇护之下\N{\rEng}I have not taken refuge behind the Fifth Amendment
Dialogue: 0,2:25:04.92,2:25:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这么做是我的权利\N{\rEng}although it is my right to do so.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.90,2:25:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我挑战本委员会\N{\rEng}I challenge this committee
Dialogue: 0,2:25:12.10,2:25:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,能提出任何对我不利的证人证物\N{\rEng}to produce any witness or evidence against me
Dialogue: 0,2:25:15.75,2:25:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们无法提出\N{\rEng}and if they do not
Dialogue: 0,2:25:18.10,2:25:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望他们有这个体面\N{\rEng}I hope they will have the decency
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.22,2:25:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,同样公开地洗刷我的名声\N{\rEng}to clear my name with the same publicity
Dialogue: 0,2:25:23.52,2:25:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在已经玷污了它\N{\rEng}with which they now have besmirched it.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:26.64,2:25:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信我们都很佩服，柯利昂尼先生\N{\rEng}I'm sure we're all quite impressed, Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:29.53,2:25:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是你对我们国家的爱\N{\rEng}Particularly with your love for our country.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.36,2:25:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将暂停到下周一上午十点\N{\rEng}We'll stand in recess until 10 a.m. Monday morning
Dialogue: 0,2:25:35.25,2:25:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我们将提出一位证人\N{\rEng}at which time we will produce a witness
Dialogue: 0,2:25:37.29,2:25:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他将证实今天对你提出的控诉\N{\rEng}who'll corroborate the charges against you today.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:40.12,2:25:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而到那时，柯利昂尼先生\N{\rEng}And at which time Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:41.96,2:25:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你非常可能会遭到伪证罪的起诉\N{\rEng}you may very well be subject to indictment for perjury.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:45.26,2:25:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我提醒你，你依然在传唤中，柯利昂尼先生\N{\rEng}I remind you that you're still under subpoena, Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:48.76,2:25:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,休会\N{\rEng}Adjourned!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:53.60,2:25:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,十比一…十比一的机会，你说的\N{\rEng}Ten-to-one...Ten-to-one shot, you said.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:56.62,2:25:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,十比一的机会\N{\rEng}Ten-to-one shot
Dialogue: 0,2:25:58.23,2:26:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他会采用第五修正案 而我输了\N{\rEng}He would take the Fifth, and I lose.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:01.60,2:26:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你听起来像是我的赌马经纪人\N{\rEng}You sound like my bookie.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:03.55,2:26:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我欠那猴子一条命\N{\rEng}I owe that monkey my life.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:07.38,2:26:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，好好睡一觉就好\N{\rEng}Well, just get a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:09.13,2:26:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，好好睡\N{\rEng}Yeah, good night sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:10.96,2:26:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是大日子\N{\rEng}You've got a big day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:13.10,2:26:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,给你买了新西装 新衬衫和新领带\N{\rEng}I've got you a new suit, new shirt, new tie.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:17.64,2:26:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我会亲自给你刮胡子\N{\rEng}I'm gonna shave you myself in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:20.96,2:26:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你的样子会很体面，在你的五千万美国同胞面前\N{\rEng}You'll look respectable for 50 million of your fellow Americans.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:25.06,2:26:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,明天，我的命…我的命过了明天就一文不值了\N{\rEng}Tomorrow... My life won't be worth a nickel after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:31.32,2:26:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧，这我看过，看过19遍了\N{\rEng}Come on! I saw this. I saw this 19 times.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:35.96,2:26:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个家很可以了，弗兰基\N{\rEng}You've got a great home here, Frankie
Dialogue: 0,2:26:38.75,2:26:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你的余生 没人能接近你\N{\rEng}for the rest of your life. Nobody gets near you
Dialogue: 0,2:26:40.90,2:26:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪里也去不了\N{\rEng}you're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:43.00,2:26:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了，那真漂亮\N{\rEng}That's great. That's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.20,2:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的好交易\N{\rEng}Some deal I made.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:48.30,2:26:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活得像国王，你会当英雄\N{\rEng}You'll live like a king. You'll be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:51.25,2:26:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里活得比外面的多数人要好\N{\rEng}You'll live better here than most people on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:54.15,2:26:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好交易\N{\rEng}Some deal!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:59.30,2:27:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,活着，潘坦吉利活着\N{\rEng}Alive. Pentangeli is alive.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:04.49,2:27:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么找上他的？\N{\rEng}How did they get their hands on him?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:06.78,2:27:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯\N{\rEng}Roth.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.63,2:27:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他设计的，迈克尔\N{\rEng}He engineered it, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:11.01,2:27:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基去跟罗萨托兄弟谈协议\N{\rEng}Frankie went to make a deal with the Rosato brothers
Dialogue: 0,2:27:13.40,2:27:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,结果他们想杀了他\N{\rEng}they tried to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:15.46,2:27:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他以为你出卖了他\N{\rEng}He thought you double-crossed him.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:18.94,2:27:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接近纽约刑警的人说 他已经半死了\N{\rEng}Our people with the New York detectives said he was half dead
Dialogue: 0,2:27:21.37,2:27:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,吓到僵硬，大声说你出卖了他\N{\rEng}scared stiff, and talking about loud that you'd turned on him.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.01,2:27:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们早就控制他了\N{\rEng}They already had him on possession
Dialogue: 0,2:27:26.51,2:27:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,做假帐 一级谋杀 还有很多罪名\N{\rEng}bookmaking, murder one and a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:31.00,2:27:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局把他隔绝了\N{\rEng}The FBI has him airtight.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:34.06,2:27:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他在一个陆军基地里，24小时警卫\N{\rEng}He's on an army base, 24 hour guards.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:37.02,2:27:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没办法接近他\N{\rEng}No way we can get to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:39.51,2:27:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你使自己涉及五项伪证罪\N{\rEng}You've opened yourself to five counts of perjury.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:44.20,2:27:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多呢？他知道什么？\N{\rEng}What about Fredo? What does he know?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:47.30,2:27:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他什么都不知道，我相信他\N{\rEng}He says he doesn't know anything and I believe him.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:51.24,2:27:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯，他…这次玩得漂亮\N{\rEng}Roth, he... played this one beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:02.80,2:28:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和弗雷多谈谈\N{\rEng}I'm want to talk to Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:44.75,2:28:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有太多可说的，麦克\N{\rEng}I haven't got a lot to say, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:49.03,2:28:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有时间\N{\rEng}We have time.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:51.93,2:28:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我相当程度被蒙在鼓里\N{\rEng}I was kept pretty much in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:56.32,2:28:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那些事我知道的不多\N{\rEng}I didn't know all that much.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:59.52,2:29:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢？\N{\rEng}What about now?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:02.36,2:29:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有什么你可以帮到我的？\N{\rEng}Is there anything you can help me out with?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:05.10,2:29:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么你现在能告诉我的？\N{\rEng}Anything you can tell me now?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:09.22,2:29:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们掌握了潘坦吉利，我只能告诉你这个\N{\rEng}They've got Pentangeli. That's all I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:26.46,2:29:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不知道会是暗杀，麦克\N{\rEng}I didn't know it was going to be a hit, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:30.27,2:29:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我对天发誓 我不知道会是暗杀\N{\rEng}I swear to God I didn't know it was going to be a hit.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:35.47,2:29:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰尼·欧拉跑来找我\N{\rEng}Johnny Ola bumped into me
Dialogue: 0,2:29:38.00,2:29:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在比佛利山\N{\rEng}in Beverly Hills.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:41.67,2:29:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 他想谈谈\N{\rEng}And he said that he wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:46.31,2:29:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他说…你和罗斯在一起做一件大买卖\N{\rEng}He said that you and Roth were in on a big deal together.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:54.95,2:29:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以在里面占一份，如果我能帮他一把的话\N{\rEng}And that there was something in it for me if I could help him out.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:59.28,2:30:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他说…他说你谈判时很顽固\N{\rEng}He said that you were being tough on the negotiations
Dialogue: 0,2:30:03.38,2:30:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果他们能得到一点帮助\N{\rEng}but if they could get a little help
Dialogue: 0,2:30:05.72,2:30:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,尽快完成这笔交易\N{\rEng}and close the deal fast
Dialogue: 0,2:30:09.36,2:30:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那会对家族有益\N{\rEng}it would be good for the family.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:13.35,2:30:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信了这个说辞？\N{\rEng}And you believed that story?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:16.32,2:30:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信那些话？\N{\rEng}You believed that?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:18.12,2:30:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他说里面有我一份\N{\rEng}He said there was something in it for me
Dialogue: 0,2:30:20.69,2:30:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,算我自己的\N{\rEng}on my own!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:22.31,2:30:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我一向都照料你，弗雷多\N{\rEng}I've always taken care of you, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:24.66,2:30:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,照料我？\N{\rEng}Taken care of me?!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:27.63,2:30:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我弟弟，你照料我？\N{\rEng}You're my kid brother!You take care of me?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:31.45,2:30:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你想过这一点吗？\N{\rEng}Did you ever think about that?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:33.20,2:30:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你有过一回想过这一点吗？\N{\rEng}Did you ever once think about that?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:36.67,2:30:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,叫弗雷多去办这个\N{\rEng}Send Fredo off to do this
Dialogue: 0,2:30:38.07,2:30:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,叫弗雷多去办那个\N{\rEng}send Fredo off to do that!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:41.37,2:30:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让弗雷多打理某地的米老鼠夜店\N{\rEng}Let Fredo take care of some Mickey Mouse nightclub somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:45.97,2:30:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,叫弗雷多去机场接谁谁\N{\rEng}Sent Fredo to take somebody at the airport!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:49.24,2:30:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你哥哥，麦克，而我却被踩在脚下\N{\rEng}I'm your older brother, Mike, and I was stepped over!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:52.32,2:30:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是爸爸想要的方式 - 那不是我要的\N{\rEng}- It's the way Pop wanted it. - It ain't the way I wanted it!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:56.91,2:30:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我能处理事情，我很聪明\N{\rEng}I can handle things, I'm smart!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:59.77,2:31:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不像每个人所说的…\N{\rEng}Not like everybody says.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:02.10,2:31:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么笨啊！我很精明 我要被尊重\N{\rEng}Like dumb. I'm smart and I want respect!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:13.78,2:31:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对这次调查 你能告诉我什么吗？\N{\rEng}Is there anything you can tell me about this investigation?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:17.59,2:31:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有吗？\N{\rEng}Anything more?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:26.85,2:31:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这个参议院律师奎斯特…\N{\rEng}The senate lawyer, Questadt...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:31.25,2:31:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他是罗斯的人\N{\rEng}He belongs to Roth.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:42.70,2:31:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷多\N{\rEng}Fredo...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:46.76,2:31:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你对我什么也不是了\N{\rEng}...you're nothing to me now.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:51.34,2:31:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是哥哥，你不是朋友\N{\rEng}You're not a brother, you're not a friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:55.50,2:31:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想知道你，或你做什么\N{\rEng}I don't want to know you, or what you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:59.72,2:32:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想看见你在那些酒店里\N{\rEng}I don't want to see you at the hotels.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:02.77,2:32:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想你接近我的房子\N{\rEng}I don't want you near my house.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:07.27,2:32:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当你要见我们的母亲时\N{\rEng}When you see our mother
Dialogue: 0,2:32:09.26,2:32:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要预先知道，好让我避开\N{\rEng}I want to know in advance, so I won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:13.47,2:32:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗？\N{\rEng}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:25.08,2:32:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,麦基\N{\rEng}Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:33.42,2:32:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要他发生任何事，只要我母亲活着的时候\N{\rEng}I don't want anything to happen to him while my mother's alive.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:27.50,2:33:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这里人比球赛还多\N{\rEng}There's more people than at a ballgame in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:31.11,2:33:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，那是威利·奇齐\N{\rEng}Hey, there's Willi Cicci!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:54.57,2:33:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,本委员会要求保持秩序\N{\rEng}This committee will come to order!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:59.96,2:34:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请说你的姓名\N{\rEng}State your name, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:01.33,2:34:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,富兰克林·潘坦吉利\N{\rEng}Franklin Pentangeli.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:02.90,2:34:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里出生？\N{\rEng}And where were you born?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:04.12,2:34:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,庞特尼格罗，在巴勒莫外面\N{\rEng}Pontenegro, it's outside of Palermo.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:06.50,2:34:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在住在哪里？\N{\rEng}Where do you live now?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:08.95,2:34:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我住在…一处军营里，和联邦调查局的人一起\N{\rEng}I live in an army barracks with the FBI guys.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:15.17,2:34:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里终于有了…\N{\rEng}We have here finally...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:17.03,2:34:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一位证人，能进一步作证…\N{\rEng}a witness will further testify
Dialogue: 0,2:34:19.70,2:34:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔·柯利昂尼统治了一个犯罪帝国\N{\rEng}to Michael Corleone's rule of a criminal empire
Dialogue: 0,2:34:22.91,2:34:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,控制全国所有的赌博，也许还有别的国家\N{\rEng}controls all of the gambling in this country. And perhaps another country.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:26.61,2:34:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这位证人没有缓冲层\N{\rEng}This witness has had no buffer
Dialogue: 0,2:34:28.54,2:34:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在他本人和迈克尔·柯利昂尼之间\N{\rEng}between himself and Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:31.10,2:34:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他能确证我们的指控有足够的依据\N{\rEng}He can corroborate our charges on enough counts
Dialogue: 0,2:34:34.54,2:34:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为本委员会提出一项 针对迈克尔·柯利昂尼的伪证罪指控\N{\rEng}for this committee to recommend a charge of perjury against Michael Corleone
Dialogue: 0,2:34:39.64,2:34:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 参议员 - 谢谢你，主席\N{\rEng}- Senator. - Thank you, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:42.81,2:34:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,潘坦吉利先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Pentangeli...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:45.77,2:34:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,潘坦吉利先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Pentangeli.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:48.33,2:34:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾是柯利昂尼家族的一员吗？\N{\rEng}Were you a member of the Corleone family?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:51.52,2:34:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否供职于分支头目彼得·克里门萨\N{\rEng}Did you serve under Caporegime, Peter Clemenza,
Dialogue: 0,2:34:56.62,2:35:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还有维多·柯利昂尼，也就是人称“教父”的\N{\rEng}and under Vito Corleone, also known as the Godfather?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:07.05,2:35:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我从不认识什么教父\N{\rEng}I never knew any Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:12.26,2:35:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我有我自己的家庭，参议员\N{\rEng}I have my own family, senator.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:17.75,2:35:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,潘坦吉利先生，你是…\N{\rEng}Mr. Pentangeli, you...
Dialogue: 0,2:35:20.25,2:35:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在反对自己先前做出并签字的宣誓陈述\N{\rEng}You are contradicting your sworn statement you previously made and signed.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:24.85,2:35:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我再问你一次 先生\N{\rEng}I ask you again, sir
Dialogue: 0,2:35:26.80,2:35:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,此时此地，在誓言之下\N{\rEng}here and now under oath,
Dialogue: 0,2:35:28.72,2:35:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾在任何时候…\N{\rEng}were you at any time...
Dialogue: 0,2:35:30.50,2:35:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,做过以迈克尔·柯利昂尼为首的犯罪组织的成员吗？\N{\rEng}a member of a crime organisation headed by Michael Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:35.00,2:35:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我对那一无所知\N{\rEng}I don't know nothing about that!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:40.90,2:35:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他父亲共事过橄榄油生意\N{\rEng}I was in the olive oil business with his father
Dialogue: 0,2:35:44.98,2:35:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是很久以前了 如此而已\N{\rEng}but that was a long time ago. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:48.64,2:35:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有份宣誓的笔录\N{\rEng}We have a sworn affidavit.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:51.83,2:35:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有，你的宣誓口供\N{\rEng}We have it. Your sworn affidavit
Dialogue: 0,2:35:54.91,2:35:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说你奉迈克尔·柯利昂尼之命搞谋杀\N{\rEng}that you murdered on the orders of Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:58.10,2:36:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否认这份自白书吗？\N{\rEng}Do you deny this confession
Dialogue: 0,2:36:00.02,2:36:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你是否了解 你的否认会有何结果？\N{\rEng}and do you realise what will happen as a result of your denial?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:02.81,2:36:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你看，调查局的人承诺我一个协议\N{\rEng}Look, the FBI guys promised me a deal
Dialogue: 0,2:36:05.95,2:36:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我…我假造了很多迈克尔·柯利昂尼的事\N{\rEng}so I made up a lot of stuff about Michael Corleone
Dialogue: 0,2:36:09.86,2:36:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那是他们想要的\N{\rEng}'cause that's what they wanted.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:11.89,2:36:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但那全是谎言\N{\rEng}But it was all lies.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:14.42,2:36:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，全都是\N{\rEng}Uh...Everything!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:16.72,2:36:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不停地说“迈克尔·柯利昂尼做了这个”\N{\rEng}They kept saying,"Michael Corleone did this"
Dialogue: 0,2:36:21.56,2:36:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,“迈克尔·柯利昂尼做了那个”\N{\rEng}and "Michael Corleone did that".
Dialogue: 0,2:36:25.40,2:36:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我说 “对，当然，有何不可？”\N{\rEng}So I said, "Yeah, sure. Why not?"
Dialogue: 0,2:36:29.73,2:36:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Corleone
Dialogue: 0,2:36:31.22,2:36:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你能否赏脸，为本委员会确认…\N{\rEng}would you kindly identify for the committee
Dialogue: 0,2:36:33.86,2:36:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,坐你左边那位先生的身份？\N{\rEng}the gentleman sitting to your left?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:35.93,2:36:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这我能回答\N{\rEng}I can answer that.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:38.33,2:36:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字是文森佐·潘坦吉利\N{\rEng}His name is Vincenzo Pentangeli.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:41.70,2:36:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他和证人有关系吗？\N{\rEng}Is he related to the witness?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:44.40,2:36:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他有，我相信是他的兄弟\N{\rEng}He is, I believe, his brother.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:46.65,2:36:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他能到前来宣誓吗？\N{\rEng}Will he come forward and be sworn?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:48.92,2:36:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，这个人不懂英语\N{\rEng}Sir, this man doesn't understand English.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:51.28,2:36:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他自费来这里 声援他兄弟所遇到的麻烦\N{\rEng}He came at his own expense to aid his brother on this kind of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:55.00,2:36:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他未被传唤\N{\rEng}He's not under subpoena
Dialogue: 0,2:36:56.30,2:36:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他的名声在他自己国家里 是毫无瑕疵的\N{\rEng}and his reputation in his own country is impeccable.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:58.84,2:37:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说他对这个人一无所知？\N{\rEng}Are you saying he knows nothing about this man?
Dialogue: 0,2:37:00.71,2:37:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,据我了解，一无所知\N{\rEng}To my knowledge, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:02.68,2:37:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我要搞清楚这是搞些什么鬼\N{\rEng}I'm going to find out what the hell happened here!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:05.44,2:37:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，本委员会现在休会\N{\rEng}All right, this committee is now adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:07.77,2:37:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,证人可以退席了\N{\rEng}The witness is excused.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:09.01,2:37:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员！\N{\rEng}Senator!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:10.82,2:37:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员！\N{\rEng}Senator!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:11.98,2:37:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个委员会应该道歉\N{\rEng}This committee owes an apology!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:14.99,2:37:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个委员会应该道歉！道歉，参议员！\N{\rEng}This committee owes an apology. Apology, Senator!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:27.59,2:37:31.25,Chs,,0,0,0,,家族的荣誉是安全的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:37:46.53,2:37:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，打扰了\N{\rEng}Michael, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:48.80,2:37:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，亲爱的\N{\rEng}Hello, darling.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:51.10,2:37:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们在外面，我们要走了\N{\rEng}The children are outside. We're going.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:55.83,2:37:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思你们要走？我们明天一起走啊\N{\rEng}What do you mean you're going? We're all gonna leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:59.51,2:38:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，洛可？\N{\rEng}Um, Rocco?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:02.80,2:38:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在我房间里，麦克\N{\rEng}I'll be in my room, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:08.14,2:38:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，我不回内华达\N{\rEng}Michael, I'm not going back to Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:11.41,2:38:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我带孩子们来跟你说再见\N{\rEng}I brought the children to say goodbye to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:17.87,2:38:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你知道 我非常为你高兴\N{\rEng}I want you to know I'm very happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:20.54,2:38:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我向来都知道 你太精明了…\N{\rEng}I suppose I always knew you were too smart...
Dialogue: 0,2:38:23.24,2:38:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让他们击败你\N{\rEng}to let any of them beat you.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:26.60,2:38:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要不坐下？ - 不，不，我不会久留，不行\N{\rEng}- Why don't you sit down? - No, I'm not going to stay long. I can.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:31.19,2:38:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有些事我想和你谈谈\N{\rEng}There are some things I'd like to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:35.49,2:38:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在我脑子里的事\N{\rEng}Things that have been on my mind
Dialogue: 0,2:38:38.83,2:38:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一些我想做的改变\N{\rEng}changes I want to make.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:40.42,2:38:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得改变已经太迟了，迈克尔\N{\rEng}I think it's too late for changes, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:44.70,2:38:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应过自己不会说什么\N{\rEng}I promised myself I wasn't going to say anything...
Dialogue: 0,2:38:47.03,2:38:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但现在…  - 你说太迟是什么意思？\N{\rEng}- but now... - What do you mean, "too late"?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:54.70,2:38:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,潘坦吉利究竟发生了何事，迈克尔？\N{\rEng}What really happened with Pentangeli?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:03.27,2:39:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他哥哥来了，帮他忙\N{\rEng}His brother came and helped him.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:05.50,2:39:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道他有个哥哥\N{\rEng}I didn't even know he had a brother.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:08.55,2:39:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在在哪里？\N{\rEng}Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:11.75,2:39:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他在飞机上，回西西里\N{\rEng}He's on a plane, back to Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:15.21,2:39:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他只要露个脸就行了\N{\rEng}All he had to do was show his face.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:19.24,2:39:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那是兄弟之间的事，凯伊\N{\rEng}It was between the brothers, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:22.31,2:39:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我与它毫不相干\N{\rEng}I had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:31.01,2:39:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔…\N{\rEng}Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:32.10,2:39:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别跟我说你要走，你不行，孩子们也不行\N{\rEng}Don't tell me you're going, Not you, not the kids
Dialogue: 0,2:39:35.12,2:39:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，你听到没？\N{\rEng}No, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:37.22,2:39:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我妻子，他们是我的孩子\N{\rEng}Now, you're my wife and they're my children
Dialogue: 0,2:39:38.85,2:39:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你，我不会允许，就是这样\N{\rEng}I love you and I won't allow, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:41.63,2:39:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你说你爱我，然后你又说“允许”我离去\N{\rEng}Michael, you say you love me, and then you talk about allowing me to leave!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:45.80,2:39:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 男女之间多年来总会有事… - 迈克尔\N{\rEng}- There're things that have been going on for years between men and women... - Micheal
Dialogue: 0,2:39:48.95,2:39:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是不会变的，就这样 - 迈克尔，你眼瞎了\N{\rEng}- that will not change and that's it. - Michael, you're blind.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:50.42,2:39:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你已经眼瞎了，迈克尔 - 对什么事瞎了？\N{\rEng}-You've become blind, Michael. - Blind of what?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:52.15,2:39:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看看，看我们间发生了什么，麦克\N{\rEng}Look! Look what's happened to us, Mike!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:54.20,2:39:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天，看看我们的儿子怎么了，迈克尔\N{\rEng}My God, Look what's happened to our son, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:56.92,2:39:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他什么事都没有 - 别告诉我没发生什么\N{\rEng}- Nothing's happened to him. - Don't tell me nothing's...
Dialogue: 0,2:39:58.56,2:40:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一切都很好 - 一切都不好\N{\rEng}- Anthony's fine. - Anthony's not fine!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:00.33,2:40:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不想听 - 你要听\N{\rEng}- I don't wanna hear about it. - You will hear about it!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:01.83,2:40:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不想听 - 没有一件事是好的\N{\rEng}- I don't wanna hear about it! - Anthony's friends...
Dialogue: 0,2:40:03.46,2:40:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不想听 - 你想骗谁？\N{\rEng}- I don't want to hear about it.- are your buttonmen!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:05.00,2:40:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想听\N{\rEng}I don't want to hear about it!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:08.07,2:40:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了\N{\rEng}Over!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:22.27,2:40:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在这一刻 我对你毫无爱意\N{\rEng}At this moment I feel no love for you at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:26.94,2:40:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没想到那会发生\N{\rEng}I never thought that would ever happen
Dialogue: 0,2:40:30.65,2:40:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但发生了\N{\rEng}but it has.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:46.15,2:40:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊\N{\rEng}Kay...
Dialogue: 0,2:40:51.38,2:40:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明天走\N{\rEng}We're leaving tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:54.15,2:40:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊，你何不带孩子回他们房间去？\N{\rEng}Why don't you take the kids back to their room?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:57.38,2:40:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你没听到我说的\N{\rEng}Michael, you haven't heard me.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:59.50,2:41:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊，你想要我怎么样？\N{\rEng}Kay, what do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:03.65,2:41:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是期望我会让你走？\N{\rEng}Do you expect me to let you go?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:05.89,2:41:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是期望我…？\N{\rEng}Do you expcet me...
Dialogue: 0,2:41:08.18,2:41:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,会让你从我身边带走我的孩子？\N{\rEng}to let you take my children from me?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:10.75,2:41:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不了解我吗？\N{\rEng}Don't you know me?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:12.00,2:41:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道那是不可能的\N{\rEng}Don't you know that's impossibility
Dialogue: 0,2:41:13.86,2:41:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不可能发生吗？\N{\rEng}that that could never happen?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:16.16,2:41:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道我会动用所有力量，阻止这种事发生吗？\N{\rEng}That I'd use all my power to keep something like that from happening?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:21.05,2:41:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道吗？\N{\rEng}Don't you know that?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:24.95,2:41:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊\N{\rEng}Kay..
Dialogue: 0,2:41:29.93,2:41:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候…\N{\rEng}In time
Dialogue: 0,2:41:32.95,2:41:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你会有不同的感受\N{\rEng}you'll feel differently.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:36.05,2:41:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你会高兴我现在阻止了你\N{\rEng}You'll be glad I stopped you now.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:40.77,2:41:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这一点\N{\rEng}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:44.88,2:41:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你因为失去胎儿而怪我\N{\rEng}I know you blame me for losing the baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:50.00,2:41:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:52.51,2:41:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道那对你有何意义\N{\rEng}I know what that meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:57.31,2:41:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我会补偿你的，凯伊\N{\rEng}I'll make it up to you, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:00.30,2:42:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓我会补偿你，我会…\N{\rEng}I swear I'll make it up to you. I'll...
Dialogue: 0,2:42:04.50,2:42:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会改变\N{\rEng}I'm going to change.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:07.65,2:42:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我会变的\N{\rEng}I'll change.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:09.70,2:42:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知道我有能力改变\N{\rEng}I've learned that I have the strength to change.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:14.04,2:42:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你将忘了这次小产\N{\rEng}Then you'll forget about this miscarriage...
Dialogue: 0,2:42:18.00,2:42:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会再有一个孩子\N{\rEng}...and we'll have another child.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:20.07,2:42:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们会走下去\N{\rEng}And we'll go on,
Dialogue: 0,2:42:21.82,2:42:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\rEng}you and I.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:24.30,2:42:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会走下去\N{\rEng}We'll go on.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:26.75,2:42:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，迈克尔\N{\rEng}Oh, Michael!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:29.60,2:42:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你眼瞎了\N{\rEng}Michael, you are blind.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:33.30,2:42:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那并不是小产\N{\rEng}It wasn't a miscarriage.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:38.10,2:42:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是堕胎\N{\rEng}It was an abortion.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:41.35,2:42:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是堕胎，迈克尔\N{\rEng}An abortion, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:44.25,2:42:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我们的婚姻一样，堕胎\N{\rEng}Just like our marriage, is an abortion.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:47.45,2:42:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一件不神圣而且邪恶的事\N{\rEng}Something that's unholy and evil!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:52.41,2:42:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要你的儿子，迈克尔\N{\rEng}I didn't want your son, Michael!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:55.90,2:43:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再把你另一个儿子带到这世上来\N{\rEng}I wouldn't bring another one of your sons into this world!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:01.42,2:43:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是堕胎，迈克尔\N{\rEng}It was an abortion, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:04.10,2:43:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个儿子，一个儿子，而我让人杀了他\N{\rEng}It was a son. A son, and I had it killed
Dialogue: 0,2:43:07.21,2:43:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这一切必须全部结束\N{\rEng}because this must all end!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:11.15,2:43:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在知道全结束了\N{\rEng}I know now that it's over.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:14.00,2:43:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我那时就知道了\N{\rEng}I knew it then.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:16.90,2:43:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没有办法了，迈克尔\N{\rEng}There would be no way, Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:43:19.10,2:43:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不可能原谅我\N{\rEng}no way you could ever forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:22.25,2:43:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为一项西西里传统 已经延续了两千年…\N{\rEng}Not with this Sicilian thing that's been going on for 2,000 years...
Dialogue: 0,2:43:34.66,2:43:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不准带走我的孩子\N{\rEng}You won't take my children.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:37.07,2:43:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\rEng}I will.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:38.10,2:43:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不准带走我的孩子 - 他们也是我的孩子\N{\rEng}- You won't take my children! - They're my children too.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:21.95,2:45:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，桑尼，你干什么？不要打架\N{\rEng}Hey, Sonny, what you doing, don't make a fight.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:20.70,2:47:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·奇西奥\N{\rEng}Don Ciccio
Dialogue: 0,2:47:22.85,2:47:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·奇西奥\N{\rEng}Don Ciccio
Dialogue: 0,2:47:27.15,2:47:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·奇西奥，是汤马西诺，唐·奇西奥\N{\rEng}Don Ciccio, Tommasino, Don Ciccio
Dialogue: 0,2:47:30.10,2:47:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·奇西奥，是汤马西诺\N{\rEng}Don Ciccio, it's Tommasino.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:31.74,2:47:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,允许我介绍一个人{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Allow me the honor of introducing someone.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:35.57,2:47:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在美国纽约的合伙人{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}My partner in America, in New York.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:38.44,2:47:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字是维多·柯利昂尼{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}His name is Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:42.37,2:47:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们由这运橄榄油给他{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}We'll send him olive oil from here.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:45.84,2:47:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,运到他美国的公司 坚科橄榄油公司{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}To his company in America.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:52.18,2:47:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们进口橄榄油，唐·奇西奥{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}They're olive oil importers, Don Ciccio.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:04.15,2:48:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·奇西奥，我们想要得到你的祝福{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}We'd like your blessing
Dialogue: 0,2:48:08.55,2:48:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,以及你许可我们工作{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}and your permission to start work.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:12.07,2:48:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这位年轻朋友由纽约来？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Where is this young man from New York?
Dialogue: 0,2:48:17.92,2:48:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他走近一点{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Have him come closer.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:22.27,2:48:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不太清楚{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}I can't see him so good.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:32.17,2:48:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·奇西奥，我向你致意{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}My respects, Don Ciccio.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:34.03,2:48:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我你的祝福{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Give me your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:38.40,2:48:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,保佑你{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Bless you!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:42.42,2:48:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,2:48:44.34,2:48:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫维多·柯利昂尼{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:46.20,2:48:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,维多·柯利昂尼{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:49.07,2:48:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你用了这村子的名字作姓氏{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}You took the name of this town!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:52.85,2:48:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲的名字呢？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}And what's your father's name?
Dialogue: 0,2:48:55.07,2:48:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字是安东尼奥·安东里尼{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}His name was... Antonio Andolini.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:58.88,2:49:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大声点，我的听力不行了{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}Louder, I don't hear so good.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:05.65,2:49:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲的名字是 安东尼奥·安东里尼{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}My father's name was Antonio Andolini...
Dialogue: 0,2:49:09.35,2:49:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而这是给你的{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}...and this is for you!
Dialogue: 0,2:50:33.80,2:50:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，说再见\N{\rEng}Mike, say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:39.67,2:51:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 艾尔\N{\rEng}Hi, Al.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:51.82,2:51:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我能与你谈一会儿吗，汤姆？\N{\rEng}Can I speak with you for a second, Tom?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:03.96,2:52:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆，麦克在哪里？\N{\rEng}Tom, where's Mike?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:06.85,2:52:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在等你离开\N{\rEng}Waiting for you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:11.70,2:52:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我能跟他谈谈吗？\N{\rEng}Can I talk with him?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:14.00,2:52:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，弗雷多，没有机会\N{\rEng}Sorry, Fredo. No chance.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:16.70,2:52:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能见他吗？ - 他在船屋里\N{\rEng}- Can I see him? - He's in the boathouse.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:33.10,2:52:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，我是康妮\N{\rEng}Michael, it's Connie.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:56.95,2:52:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\rEng}Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:53:01.65,2:53:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在想住得离家近些了，如果可以的话\N{\rEng}I'd like to stay close to home now, if it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:13.42,2:53:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊会来吗？\N{\rEng}Is Kay coming?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:18.63,2:53:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:27.60,2:53:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，弗雷多在屋子里陪妈妈\N{\rEng}Michael, Fredo's in the house with Mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:31.05,2:53:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他要求见你，汤姆说…\N{\rEng}He asked for you and Tom said...
Dialogue: 0,2:53:33.76,2:53:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不愿见他\N{\rEng}you wouldn't see him.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:38.30,2:53:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:43.07,2:53:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们，你们要不到外面去一会儿？\N{\rEng}Kids, why don't you go outside for a while?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:50.14,2:53:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，拜托，我想和你谈谈\N{\rEng}Michael, please, I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:54:03.75,2:54:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔，我恨过你…很多年来\N{\rEng}Michael, I hated you for so many years.
Dialogue: 0,2:54:08.70,2:54:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我对自己做这些事…\N{\rEng}I think I did things to myself
Dialogue: 0,2:54:11.45,2:54:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,伤害我自己，从而让你知道…\N{\rEng}to hurt myself so that you'd know
Dialogue: 0,2:54:17.25,2:54:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我能够伤到你\N{\rEng}that I could hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,2:54:25.40,2:54:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是…\N{\rEng}You were just...
Dialogue: 0,2:54:26.83,2:54:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我们大家而坚强，像爸爸以前那样\N{\rEng}being strong for all of us, the way Papa was.
Dialogue: 0,2:54:30.55,2:54:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我原谅了你\N{\rEng}And I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,2:54:36.85,2:54:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能原谅弗雷多吗？\N{\rEng}Can't you forgive Fredo?
Dialogue: 0,2:54:39.93,2:54:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他那么可爱…\N{\rEng}He's so sweet
Dialogue: 0,2:54:42.10,2:54:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你是那么的无助\N{\rEng}and helpless without you.
Dialogue: 0,2:54:50.85,2:54:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要我，迈克尔\N{\rEng}You need me, Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:54:52.45,2:54:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在想来照顾你\N{\rEng}I want to take care of you now.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:04.42,2:55:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,康妮\N{\rEng}Connie...
Dialogue: 0,2:56:48.30,2:56:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆，坐\N{\rEng}Tom, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:55.66,2:56:56.62,Chs,,0,0,0,,怎么了？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:56:58.20,2:56:59.62,Chs,,0,0,0,,没事啊，为什么问？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:57:02.67,2:57:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的朋友兼生意伙伴，海门·罗斯上报了\N{\rEng}Our friend and business partner,Hyman Roth, is in the news.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:07.67,2:57:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,2:57:10.04,2:57:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说他在以色列\N{\rEng}I hear that he's in Israel.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:13.01,2:57:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以色列的高等法院\N{\rEng}The High Court in Israel
Dialogue: 0,2:57:14.51,2:57:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,驳回了他做为回归犹太人的居住申请\N{\rEng}turned down his request to live there as a return jew.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:17.74,2:57:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他的护照被宣布无效，只好回美国来\N{\rEng}His passport's been invalidated, except to return to the U.S
Dialogue: 0,2:57:21.38,2:57:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他昨天在布宜诺斯艾利斯着陆\N{\rEng}He landed in Buenos Aires yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:24.35,2:57:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他提出一份百万美元大礼，只要他们允许他在那里居住\N{\rEng}He offered a gift of a million dollars if they'd let him live there.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:29.31,2:57:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们回绝了他\N{\rEng}They turned him down.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:31.52,2:57:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他打算尝试巴拿马\N{\rEng}He's going to try Panama.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:33.70,2:57:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,巴拿马不会接受他的\N{\rEng}Panama won't take him.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:35.64,2:57:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一百万或一千万都不行\N{\rEng}Not for a million, not for ten million
Dialogue: 0,2:57:38.55,2:57:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他的状况报告为晚期\N{\rEng}His condition is reported as terminal.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:40.42,2:57:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,反正只能再活六个月\N{\rEng}He's only gonna live another six months anyway.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:43.41,2:57:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他的心脏病让他垂死快20年了\N{\rEng}He's dieing at the same heart attack for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:46.51,2:57:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他坐飞机飞往迈阿密\N{\rEng}That plane goes to Miami.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:48.45,2:57:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，我就是要在那儿下手\N{\rEng}That's right. That's where I want it met.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:51.92,2:57:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，那是不可能的\N{\rEng}Mike, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:53.60,2:57:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会把他直接交给国税部门\N{\rEng}They'll turn him over directly to the Internal Revenue
Dialogue: 0,2:57:55.59,2:57:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,海关以及联邦调查局\N{\rEng}Customs and FBI.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:57.53,2:57:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不是不可能的\N{\rEng}It's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:59.71,2:58:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么是不可能的\N{\rEng}Nothing's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:00.90,2:58:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就像想刺杀总统一样\N{\rEng}It will be like trying to kill the president.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:02.35,2:58:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没办法接近他\N{\rEng}There's no way we can get to him!
Dialogue: 0,2:58:04.26,2:58:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆，你现在让我惊讶了\N{\rEng}Tom, now you surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:09.56,2:58:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这生命中有什么确定的事\N{\rEng}If anything in this life is certain...
Dialogue: 0,2:58:13.22,2:58:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果历史教给我们什么\N{\rEng}...if history has taught us anything...
Dialogue: 0,2:58:16.53,2:58:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你可以杀任何人\N{\rEng}...it's that you can kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:24.40,2:58:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,洛可？\N{\rEng}Rocco?
Dialogue: 0,2:58:26.43,2:58:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,困难，不是不可能\N{\rEng}Difficult. Not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:29.74,2:58:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:34.01,2:58:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我进来时你为什么问我是不是有事？\N{\rEng}Why did you ask me if something was wrong when I came in?
Dialogue: 0,2:58:41.35,2:58:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你会告诉我…\N{\rEng}I thought you were going to tell me
Dialogue: 0,2:58:44.91,2:58:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把你家搬去维加斯\N{\rEng}that you're moving your family to Vegas
Dialogue: 0,2:58:48.65,2:58:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有人请你去当 休斯顿饭店的副总裁\N{\rEng}and that you'd been offered the Vice Presidency of the Houstan hotels there.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:54.39,2:58:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我以为你会告诉我这事 - 我拒绝了他们\N{\rEng}- I thought you'd tell me that. - I turned them down.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:56.31,2:58:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，我必须告诉你我拒绝的每一个邀约吗？\N{\rEng}I mean must I tell you every offer I turn down?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:03.56,2:59:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们谈正事吧 - 好的\N{\rEng}- Let's do business. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:08.03,2:59:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只要考虑一下，麦克，考虑一下\N{\rEng}Just consider this, Mike, that's all. Just consider it.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:12.30,2:59:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯和罗萨托兄弟正在跑路\N{\rEng}Now, Roth and the Rosatos are on the run.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:14.59,2:59:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们值得吗，我们够强吗？\N{\rEng}Are they worth it, are we strong enough?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:17.80,2:59:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这样值不值？\N{\rEng}Is it worth it?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:20.10,2:59:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说你赢了 你还想要干掉每一个人\N{\rEng}I mean you've won. Do you want to wipe everybody out?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:22.63,2:59:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得我需要干掉每一个人，汤姆\N{\rEng}I don't feel I have to wipe everybody out, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:26.55,2:59:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我的敌人，如此而已\N{\rEng}Just my enemies, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:35.47,2:59:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是支持我做我必须做的事情，还是怎样？\N{\rEng}Are you gonna come alone with me in these things I have to do, or what?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:40.45,2:59:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果不支持\N{\rEng}Because if not
Dialogue: 0,2:59:41.47,2:59:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以带着你妻子、你的家人…\N{\rEng}you can take your wife, your family
Dialogue: 0,2:59:44.55,2:59:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,及你的情妇们\N{\rEng}and your mistress
Dialogue: 0,2:59:46.34,2:59:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,全部搬到拉斯维加斯去\N{\rEng}and move them all to Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:52.45,2:59:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么伤害我，迈克尔？\N{\rEng}Why do you hurt me, Michael?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:54.37,2:59:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我一向对你忠诚\N{\rEng}I've always been loyal to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:55.51,2:59:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说…这算什么？\N{\rEng}I mean...what is this?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:02.18,3:00:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…你留下来？{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}So... you're staying?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:05.58,3:00:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是，我留下{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r} - 好{\fs12}[意大利语]{\r}\N{\rEng}- Yes, I'm staying. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:10.92,3:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 你要我做的是什么事？\N{\rEng}What is it do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:13.50,3:00:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，安东尼\N{\rEng}Hey, Anthony
Dialogue: 0,3:00:15.84,3:00:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，安东尼，你想不想要我…\N{\rEng}Hey, Anthony, how would you like it if I...
Dialogue: 0,3:00:17.93,3:00:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你想不想要我教你如何抓真正的大鱼 如何？\N{\rEng}How would you like it if I taught you how to catch the really big fish?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:20.57,3:00:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想学吗？ - 好\N{\rEng}- Would you like that? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:23.39,3:00:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 我在你这个年纪时\N{\rEng}You know, when I was your age...
Dialogue: 0,3:00:26.25,3:00:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我所有的兄弟一起去钓鱼\N{\rEng}...I went out fishing with all my brothers
Dialogue: 0,3:00:29.99,3:00:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…还有我父亲，大家一起\N{\rEng}and my father. Everybody.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:34.42,3:00:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而我…我是唯一钓到鱼的\N{\rEng}I was the only one that caught a fish.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:38.82,3:00:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再没别人钓到，除了我\N{\rEng}Nobody else could catch one exept me.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:41.38,3:00:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我怎么做到的？\N{\rEng}Do you know how I did it?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:44.66,3:00:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次我把钓线丢入水中时\N{\rEng}Every time I put the line in the water
Dialogue: 0,3:00:46.46,3:00:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我说万福玛利亚\N{\rEng}I said a Hail Mary
Dialogue: 0,3:00:48.53,3:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,每次我说万福玛利亚 我都钓到鱼\N{\rEng}and every time I said a Hail Mary, I caught a fish.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:54.60,3:00:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信吗？\N{\rEng}Do you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:56.30,3:00:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的，这就是秘诀\N{\rEng}It's true. That's the secret.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:00.80,3:01:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到湖上时 你想试试吗？\N{\rEng}Do you want to try it out on the lake?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:02.80,3:01:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 - 好\N{\rEng}- Okay.- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:06.50,3:01:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你还带了什么？\N{\rEng}What else have you got?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:34.66,3:01:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好的，弗兰基，别担心\N{\rEng}Everything will be okay, Frankie, dont' worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:36.98,3:01:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥回去了吗？\N{\rEng}Did my brother go back?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:38.36,3:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，别担心\N{\rEng}Yeah, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:41.20,3:01:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他比我坚强十倍，我哥哥\N{\rEng}He's ten times tougher than me, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:44.40,3:01:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他是老派的人 - 对\N{\rEng}-He's old-fashioned. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:47.33,3:01:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他连出去吃晚饭都不肯\N{\rEng}He didn't want to go dinner
Dialogue: 0,3:01:48.67,3:01:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他只想直接回家\N{\rEng}just wanted to go straight home.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:50.60,3:01:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我哥哥\N{\rEng}That's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,3:01:51.76,3:01:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何事能让他离开那二骡小镇\N{\rEng}Nothing could get him away from that two-mule town.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:55.63,3:01:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他本可以在这里做大，他本可以有自己的家族\N{\rEng}He could have been big here. He could have had his own family.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:04.87,3:02:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆\N{\rEng}Tom
Dialogue: 0,3:02:07.51,3:02:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在该怎么做？\N{\rEng}what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,3:02:10.74,3:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基\N{\rEng}Frankie
Dialogue: 0,3:02:17.27,3:02:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你一向对政治和历史有兴趣\N{\rEng}You were always interested in politics and history.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:22.94,3:02:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你谈过33年的希特勒\N{\rEng}I remember you talking about Hitler back in '33.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:26.50,3:02:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我仍然读很多书，我在里面有好书\N{\rEng}Yeah, I still read a lot. I get good stuff in there.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:32.62,3:02:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾在老一辈身边\N{\rEng}You were around the old-timers
Dialogue: 0,3:02:35.28,3:02:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是如何把家族组织起来的\N{\rEng}who built how the families to be organised
Dialogue: 0,3:02:38.24,3:02:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们如何以古罗马军团为基础\N{\rEng}how to base them on the old Roman legions
Dialogue: 0,3:02:40.18,3:02:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还称之为“政体”、“头目”和“军士”\N{\rEng}and called them "regimes", "capos" and "soldiers".
Dialogue: 0,3:02:45.32,3:02:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而且奏效了\N{\rEng}And it worked.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:47.30,3:02:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，是奏效了\N{\rEng}Yeah, it worked.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:50.15,3:02:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是伟大的老日子 你知道吗？\N{\rEng}Those were the great old days, you know.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:53.65,3:02:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就像是罗马帝国\N{\rEng}We was like the Roman Empire.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:56.90,3:03:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼家族就像是罗马帝国\N{\rEng}The Corleone family was like the Roman Empire.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:02.80,3:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,3:03:05.00,3:03:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,它一度是\N{\rEng}it was once.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:11.46,3:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基\N{\rEng}Frankie
Dialogue: 0,3:03:23.71,3:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当一场反对帝国的阴谋失败时\N{\rEng}When a plot against the Emperor failed...
Dialogue: 0,3:03:28.50,3:03:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,阴谋者总是被给予一次机会…\N{\rEng}...the plotters were always given a chance...
Dialogue: 0,3:03:33.87,3:03:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让自己的家族保有财富\N{\rEng}...to let their families keep their fortunes.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:37.11,3:03:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对？\N{\rEng}Right?
Dialogue: 0,3:03:37.77,3:03:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对，但那只是有钱人，汤姆\N{\rEng}Yeah, but only the rich guys, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:39.82,3:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小人物呢，他们被干掉\N{\rEng}The little guys, they got knocked off
Dialogue: 0,3:03:42.04,3:03:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们所有的不动产归于皇帝\N{\rEng}and all their estates went to the Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:44.65,3:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,除非他们回家自杀\N{\rEng}Unless they went home and killed themselves
Dialogue: 0,3:03:48.00,3:03:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不会发生任何事\N{\rEng}then nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:51.12,3:03:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而他们的家庭\N{\rEng}And their families
Dialogue: 0,3:03:53.20,3:03:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的家庭会被照顾，汤姆\N{\rEng}their families were taken care of, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:57.35,3:04:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个好的机会，好交易\N{\rEng}That was a good break, a nice deal.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:01.48,3:04:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:03.65,3:04:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们…他们回到家里\N{\rEng}They...they went home...
Dialogue: 0,3:04:07.05,3:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在热水浴缸里\N{\rEng}and sat in a hot bath
Dialogue: 0,3:04:10.05,3:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,割开血管，流血至死\N{\rEng}opened up their veins and bled to death.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:16.70,3:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且有时候他们这么做之前，还会有个小派对\N{\rEng}And sometimes they had a little party before they did it.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:25.96,3:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心任何事，弗兰基五天使\N{\rEng}Don't worry about anything, Frankie Five-Angels.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:30.05,3:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，汤姆，谢了\N{\rEng}Thanks, Tom. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:51.70,3:04:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再见，汤姆\N{\rEng}See you, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:52.93,3:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了，弗兰克\N{\rEng}Addio, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,3:05:05.75,3:05:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊 你必须走了\N{\rEng}Kay... You have to go.
Dialogue: 0,3:05:10.45,3:05:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,多漂亮\N{\rEng}So pretty
Dialogue: 0,3:05:11.56,3:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊，请快点，他来了\N{\rEng}Kay, please hurry. He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,3:05:22.85,3:05:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼\N{\rEng}Anthony...
Dialogue: 0,3:05:25.14,3:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,和妈妈吻别\N{\rEng}Kiss Mama goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,3:05:29.23,3:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼，你去不去跟妈妈吻别？\N{\rEng}Anthony, would you kiss your mother good bye.
Dialogue: 0,3:05:32.19,3:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼，跟妈妈说再见，安东尼\N{\rEng}Anthony,say good bye to mama, Anthony
Dialogue: 0,3:05:35.40,3:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你，亲爱的\N{\rEng}I love you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,3:05:38.63,3:05:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,凯伊，拜托！\N{\rEng}Kay, please.
Dialogue: 0,3:05:43.84,3:05:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…好吧\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,3:05:58.47,3:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,玛莉 到这来\N{\rEng}Mary, come here.
Dialogue: 0,3:06:08.02,3:06:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼，请你就吻我一次\N{\rEng}Anthony, please. Kiss me once.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:52.19,3:07:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 接稳了\N{\rEng}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:59.96,3:08:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼…安东尼\N{\rEng}Anthony! Anthony!
Dialogue: 0,3:08:03.24,3:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这里，我们要去钓鱼\N{\rEng}He's here we're going fishing!
Dialogue: 0,3:08:05.42,3:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不，麦克现在要带他去雷诺\N{\rEng}No. Michael want to take him to Reno now.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:09.67,3:08:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，可恶\N{\rEng}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,3:08:13.06,3:08:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，孩子，你得和你爸爸去雷诺\N{\rEng}Okay, kid, you have to go to Reno with your pop.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:17.60,3:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，安东尼，我明天再带你去钓鱼，好吗？\N{\rEng}Come on, Anthony, I'll take you fishing tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,3:08:20.61,3:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:23.94,3:08:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子\N{\rEng}That a boy.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:25.35,3:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，安东尼\N{\rEng}Hey, Anthony
Dialogue: 0,3:08:27.00,3:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，我悄悄为你钓一条鱼\N{\rEng}Listen, I'll catch one for you in secret.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:30.79,3:08:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吗？ - 好\N{\rEng}- All right? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:31.74,3:08:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，去吧\N{\rEng}All right, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:34.45,3:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，艾尔，我们走\N{\rEng}Okay, Al, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:15.78,3:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯先生，你了解我必须把你收押吗？\N{\rEng}Mr. Roth, you understand I'll have to take you into custody.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:18.35,3:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我了解\N{\rEng}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:20.02,3:09:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你能否跟我们说说 你对以色列高等法院裁决的反应？\N{\rEng}Can you give us what's your reaction to the High Court of Israeli ruling?
Dialogue: 0,3:09:23.22,3:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一个退休拿津贴的投资者\N{\rEng}I'm a retired investor on a pension.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:26.42,3:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我去以色列是因为 我希望作为犹太人在那里居住\N{\rEng}I went to Israel because I wish to live there as a Jew
Dialogue: 0,3:09:30.08,3:09:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,安度晚年\N{\rEng}in the twilight of my life.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:37.75,3:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基，出来，我们来玩红心大战\N{\rEng}Hey, Frankie! Come on out, let's play some Hearts.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:49.71,3:09:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基\N{\rEng}Frankie!
Dialogue: 0,3:10:07.01,3:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身家真的超过三亿美金，罗斯先生？\N{\rEng}Is it true you're worth over 300 million dollars, Mr. Roth?
Dialogue: 0,3:10:10.39,3:10:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我是退休的投资者，靠养老金过活\N{\rEng}I'm a retired investor, living on a pension.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:13.95,3:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我回家来参加总统大选投票\N{\rEng}I came home to vote in the presidential election
Dialogue: 0,3:10:17.73,3:10:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们不给我 一张缺席的选举票\N{\rEng}because they wouldn't give me an absentee ballot.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:25.46,3:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,站住！\N{\rEng}Halt!
Dialogue: 0,3:10:33.50,3:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\rEng}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:37.00,3:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,万福玛利亚，充满恩惠\N{\rEng}Hail Mary, full of grace.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:40.37,3:10:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,主与汝同在\N{\rEng}The Lord is with thee.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:42.73,3:10:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,赐福予汝等之妇女\N{\rEng}Blessed art thou amongst women.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:46.31,3:10:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,赐福乃孕育于汝子宫之胎，基督\N{\rEng}Blessed is the fruit of thy womb, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:50.87,3:10:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,神圣玛利亚，上帝之母，为我等罪人祈祷\N{\rEng}Holy Mary, Mother of God, pray for us sinners.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:36.86,3:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，大家快点，注意了\N{\rEng}Hey! Everybody, come on, pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:39.46,3:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\rEng}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:40.70,3:11:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我朋友卡洛·瑞兹\N{\rEng}This is my friend Carlo Rizzi.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:42.70,3:11:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我弟弟弗雷多，哦，你认识他的\N{\rEng}You know my brother Fredo. Oh, you know him.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:44.13,3:11:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，我…\N{\rEng}Sure, I...
Dialogue: 0,3:11:45.83,3:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的养兄弟汤姆\N{\rEng}This is my stepbrother Tom
Dialogue: 0,3:11:47.80,3:11:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他的女友泰瑞莎\N{\rEng}and that's his girl Theresa.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:50.55,3:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这里这个可人儿是我妹妹康妮\N{\rEng}This cute little thing over here is my sister Connie.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:52.47,3:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你提起过的\N{\rEng}I told you about that.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:53.91,3:11:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来，跟卡洛打招呼\N{\rEng}Come on, say hello to Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:55.73,3:11:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他很帅，对吧？ - 是的\N{\rEng}- He's good-looking? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:58.58,3:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，那边那个打蔫儿的傢伙，是我弟弟麦克\N{\rEng}Oh, that droopy thing over there, that's my brother Mike.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:01.27,3:12:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们叫他大学生，知道我的意思吧\N{\rEng}We call him Joe College, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,3:12:03.20,3:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 坐吧 彼此谈谈 - 坐吧\N{\rEng}- Come on, sit down. Talk to each other. - Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:07.17,3:12:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，爱因斯坦先生…\N{\rEng}Hey, Mr. Einstein...
Dialogue: 0,3:12:12.78,3:12:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蛋糕来了 - 嘿，萨利，进来\N{\rEng}- The cake. - Hey, Sally, get in here!
Dialogue: 0,3:12:15.41,3:12:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- …我都吓着了 - 来吧！\N{\rEng}- I was scared. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:18.35,3:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲在哪里？\N{\rEng}Where's your father?
Dialogue: 0,3:12:19.51,3:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 得有一会儿，他去做圣诞节采购 - 放这里\N{\rEng}- It's gonna be a while, Christmas shopping. - Put here.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:21.85,3:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看看那东西\N{\rEng}Let's see that thing.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:25.35,3:12:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，康妮，真漂亮\N{\rEng}Oh, Connie, that's nice!
Dialogue: 0,3:12:27.86,3:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我应该现在插蜡烛吗？ - 插吧\N{\rEng}- Should I put the candles on now? - Yea go on.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:29.75,3:12:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你帮她好吗，卡洛？ - 当然\N{\rEng}- Yeah. You help her, Carlo. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:31.89,3:12:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 泰西欧\N{\rEng}Hello,Tessio.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:33.05,3:12:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？兰姆酒吗？\N{\rEng}What is that? Rum?
Dialogue: 0,3:12:34.32,3:12:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说是\N{\rEng}Yeah, that's what they call it.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:40.95,3:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,桑尼，得了，爸爸回来前别碰餐前点\N{\rEng}Sonny, come on, don't touch the anti-pasta until Pop gets here.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:44.46,3:12:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他不丑吗？\N{\rEng}He's not ugly?
Dialogue: 0,3:12:52.60,3:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们说日本人的胆量如何？那帮眯眯眼的杂种\N{\rEng}What do you think of the nerve of those Japs? those slanty eyed bastards, huh.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:56.23,3:12:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸生日这天往我们后院扔炸弹{\fs12}[珍珠港事件]{\r}\N{\rEng}Dropping bombs in outown back yard and on Pops birthday ya know.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:58.63,3:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们并不知道是爸爸生日 - 他们并不知道是爸爸生日\N{\rEng}- Now they didn't know it was Pop's birthday. - They didn't know it was Pop's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:02.50,3:13:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在石油禁运之后，我们就该料到的\N{\rEng}We should have expected after the oil embargo.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:05.10,3:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么料到？料到什么啊？\N{\rEng}What do you mean expect it, expected nothing
Dialogue: 0,3:13:06.44,3:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有权利扔炸弹\N{\rEng}they got no right dropping bombs.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:07.88,3:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么？站他们那边的亲日分子？\N{\rEng}What are you? A Jap lover or something are you on their side?
Dialogue: 0,3:13:09.88,3:13:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道今早有三万人应征入伍\N{\rEng}I understand 30,000 enlisted this morning.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:12.14,3:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一群笨蛋\N{\rEng}Bunch of saps
Dialogue: 0,3:13:13.53,3:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么是笨蛋？\N{\rEng}Why are they saps?
Dialogue: 0,3:13:15.03,3:13:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,桑尼 别这样 我们不必谈论战争\N{\rEng}Sonny,come on.We don't have to talk about the war.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:17.24,3:13:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，走开，你去跟卡洛聊天，好不好？\N{\rEng}Hey beat it, you go talk to Carlo alright.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:21.98,3:13:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是笨蛋\N{\rEng}They're saps
Dialogue: 0,3:13:23.39,3:13:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们为陌生人冒生命危险\N{\rEng}because they risk their lives for strangers.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:25.66,3:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是爸爸的语气\N{\rEng}Now that's Pop talking..
Dialogue: 0,3:13:26.81,3:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也没错，那是爸爸的语气\N{\rEng}You're god damn right that's Pop talking.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:29.33,3:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为国家冒生命危险\N{\rEng}They risk their lives for their country.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:31.25,3:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,国家不是你的血脉 你要记住\N{\rEng}Country isn't your blood, you remember that.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:33.21,3:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得是那样\N{\rEng}I don't feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:34.38,3:13:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得是那样\N{\rEng}Well if you don't fell that way
Dialogue: 0,3:13:35.35,3:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不觉得是那样，你为何不休学去从军呢？\N{\rEng}Well, if you don't feel like that, why don't you just quit collage and go to...go to join the Army.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:39.15,3:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了\N{\rEng}I did.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:41.65,3:13:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我加入了陆战队\N{\rEng}I've enlisted in the Marines.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:46.69,3:13:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，为什么？你为什么不来找我们？\N{\rEng}Mike, why? Why didn't you come to us?
Dialogue: 0,3:13:49.49,3:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思？\N{\rEng}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,3:13:50.69,3:13:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说爸爸不得不动用了很多关系 让你缓服兵役\N{\rEng}I mean Pop had to pull a lot of strings to get you a deferment.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:53.32,3:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我没要那样\N{\rEng}I didn't ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:55.15,3:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有要缓服兵役，我并不想要\N{\rEng}I didn't ask for deferment and I didn't want it.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:58.00,3:14:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是怎么一回事 - 别这样!…别打了\N{\rEng}- What's wrong? - Come on! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,3:14:01.12,3:14:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 桑尼 - 混蛋\N{\rEng}- Sonny - Punk!
Dialogue: 0,3:14:02.59,3:14:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 桑尼，坐下  - 坐，坐下\N{\rEng}- Sonny, sit down. - Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:07.66,3:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,妈咪，爸爸又在打架了！\N{\rEng}Mommy, Daddy's fighting again!
Dialogue: 0,3:14:14.40,3:14:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,去给卡洛看看圣诞树\N{\rEng}Go and show Carlo the tree.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:21.42,3:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔叔叔 妈妈 爸爸\N{\rEng}Uncle Miclael, mama, dady.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:26.97,3:14:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮\N{\rEng}Nice
Dialogue: 0,3:14:30.67,3:14:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮\N{\rEng}Nice
Dialogue: 0,3:14:33.37,3:14:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在你父亲的生日上伤他的心\N{\rEng}break your father's heart on his birthday.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:36.81,3:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好，麦克，恭喜你\N{\rEng}That's swell, Mike. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:39.61,3:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊，鼓励他\N{\rEng}That's right, encourage him.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:41.65,3:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你给我拿杯酒，去吧\N{\rEng}I want you to get me a drink, go on.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:48.75,3:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,麦基，你还不知道，但你父亲对你有计划的\N{\rEng}Mickey, you don't understand but, uh, your father has big plans for you.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:51.98,3:14:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很多次…他都提到了你的未来\N{\rEng}Now many times he and I have talked about your future.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:58.15,3:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟我父亲谈我的未来？ - 是的\N{\rEng}- Talked to my father about my future? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:03.42,3:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的未来？\N{\rEng}My future?
Dialogue: 0,3:15:04.69,3:15:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,麦基，他对你期望很高\N{\rEng}Mikey, he has high hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:07.65,3:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我对我的未来有自己的计划\N{\rEng}Well I have my own plans for my future.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:10.55,3:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？你上大学上傻了？你真是犯傻\N{\rEng}What'd you go to collage to get stupid? You're really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:13.36,3:15:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他回来了 快点\N{\rEng}He's here come on.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:17.20,3:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧…来吧\N{\rEng}Come on...
Dialogue: 0,3:15:21.32,3:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,傻\N{\rEng}Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,3:15:40.60,3:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大惊喜\N{\rEng}Surprise!

